This documentary looks back on the life of legendary flamenco singer Camarón, who went from humble roots to rock star status to a tragic early death.
In the probing documentary "Party Monster," DJ Fingablast investigates what became of his childhood hero, DJ Slizzard.
In his hometown of Toronto, Shawn Mendes pours his heart out on stage with a live performance in a stadium packed with adoring fans.
Disgusted by the gold-chain snatchers in his home city of Chennai, a man vows to combat the criminal menace by taking the law into his own hands.
As Ayu and Ditto finally transition from best friends to newlyweds, a quick pregnancy creates uncertainty for the future of their young marriage.

Titulo: Marvel Super Hero Adventures: Frost Fight!
Enredo: In this Christmas-themed special, Captain America and the Avengers battle Loki and Ymir, who plot to steal Santa Claus' powers and conquer the world.

Titulo: My Way: The Rise and Fall of Silvio Berlusconi

Enredo: When caste differences throw a wrench into their otherwise blossoming relationship, a couple must somehow convince the girl’s father to let them marry.

Titulo: Rhys Nicholson: Live at the Athenaeum

Enredo: Honest, introspective comic Simon Amstell digs deep and delivers a uniquely vulnerable stand-up set on love, ego, intimacy and ayahuasca.
Sick of his parents’ constant squabbling, a young man travels back in time to the onset of their romance, with plans to set them up for marital bliss.
In this jailhouse interview, Arthur Shawcross, the Genesee River Killer, shares candid details of his crimes and his surprising family bonds.
Stranded at school before holiday break, a precocious girl gets into the spirit of saving when a trio of robbers trespass and hold the janitor hostage.

Titulo: The Return of the Prodigal Son

Enredo: Outcast from society and left to die in the wilderness, a young boy with polio embarks on a journey to connect with his mother. Based on a true story.
Concert and behind-the-scenes footage capture life on tour for Uruguayan sensation Natalia Oreiro as she performs for packed crowds throughout Russia.

Titulo: Zip & Zap and the Captain's Island

Enredo: Two young artists, a violin player and an actress, fight to achieve their dreams and keep their relationship together during Christmastime.
When a man discovers that he can communicate with his grandfather's spirit, it leads to two love stories intertwining 50 years apart.
A simple village man is thrown into a web of political intrigue after he takes on a powerful and ruthless gang of bandits.
Mexican comic Carlos Ballarta mocks himself and points out the absurdities of parenthood and how he uses his wife's pregnancies to avoid commitments.

Titulo: Casablancas: The Man Who Loved Women
Enredo: The rise and smash success of Elite modeling agency founder John Casablancas is chronicled in this biography of the man who invented the supermodel.
Having risen from humble beginnings, an ambitious young man sets his sights on winning a major dance competition that could catapult him to fame.
A special agent abruptly reunites with a criminal – once a former friend – when he attempts to use his identity to infiltrate and take down a cartel.
A professor mysteriously vanishes, leaving behind a host of suspects, a shadowy history and a clue: the anonymous birthday gift of a Bengali classic.
Without fully realizing the consequences, a boy who wants to relocate from India to Canada sells his heart to a gangster in need of a transplant.
After his affluent father passes, a man must survive seven days in the Nigerian neighborhood of Ajegunle, where obstacles keep him from his inheritance.
In this quiet, wistful drama, a woman on her deathbed searches her fraying memories for love and fulfillment through surreal, meditative tableaux.
New York comedian Colin Quinn writes and stars in this live one-man stage show that dissects and deconstructs U.S. constitutional history.
After tracing an artifact to his ancestry, a young man and his friend's search for a gilded statue lands them in a maximum-security prison.

Titulo: Belief: The Possession of Janet Moses
Enredo: This documentary tries to reconstruct, through a series of interviews, a family's misguided attempt to heal a woman's pain through exorcism.

Titulo: Kenny Sebastian: The Most Interesting Person in the Room
Enredo: Fusing his musical and stand-up chops, Kenny Sebastian gets analytical about frumpy footwear, flightless birds and his fear of not being funny enough.
An international group of filmmakers sets out on a mission to get up close and personal with a family of elusive snow leopards.
The world's got a lot of problems, but Vir Das has a lot of answers as he discusses travel, religion, his childhood and more in this stand-up special.
Fernando is a family man — equally committed to each of his two families. But one wrong turn brings them crashing together.
Sisters Mia and Emma move to their grandmother’s farm far from the city and save a magical unicorn from local cowboys seeking its powers for themselves.
After searching for his abducted son for three years, a devastated father attempts to track down his missing child through lucid dreams.
In a last-ditch effort, the jaded coach of the Southall United Football Club assembles a ragtag team and helps lead the team to a comeback season.
Ambitious Kunal takes a job in the diamond business, but his life is thrown into turmoil when he's drawn into the seedy underworld of his new career.
Comic Moshe Kasher returns to his home turf of Oakland for this stand-up special that has him sharing uproarious stories about the people he's met.
With unlimited determination and zero field experience, a small-town detective accepts a lucrative case from a mysterious – and suspicious – stranger.
In this documentary, female office workers in '70s Boston inspire change with a call for better pay, more opportunities and an end to sexual harassment.
Five youngsters discover that an antique mirror found in their orphanage is home to an evil ghost who kidnaps children and imprisons them inside it.
With the guidance of her relentless coach, a teen weightlifter emerges from a scrappy training camp in Egypt to compete at the championship level.
Trying to uphold justice in a lawless future, a D.A. is slain by cyberpunks but a supernatural twist sends his car on a bloody quest for revenge.
Three youths from rural South Africa set out for Johannesburg, where they're thrust into the seedy underbelly of the city and must fight to survive.
Chipper baby boomer Kath, diva daughter Kim and hapless pal Sharon visit Papilloma, Italy, where a royal romance and knockoff fashions await.
Following a tragedy, a mother and her teen son move to a relative's vacant vacation home, where eerie and unexplained forces conspire against them.
After being wrongfully convicted of fraud, an honest man finds that life in prison comes with a measure of freedom that is unavailable outside.
Urban comic Katt Williams ushers in Kattpacalypse, exploding with more energy than an atomic bomb and riffing on everything from Doomsday to Obama.
A high-flying rock star and son of a politician falls for a woman from a qawwal family, leading to a love triangle that may consume everyone involved.
After his sleeping disorder hinders him from protecting his girlfriend, a man sets out to take revenge on the thugs who attacked her.

Titulo: Hikaru Utada Laughter in the Dark Tour 2018
Enredo: Celebrating twenty years since her debut, Hikaru Utada takes the stage at Makuhari Messe for the final performance of her Laughter in the Dark Tour.
When a narco past his prime refuses to pay a debt to an upstart, only a secret stash of money can save his men. But guess what the gardener just found?
The residents of an isolated town look to revive their home's identity when a group of foreigners unexpectedly arrive, bringing culture shock with them.
Pining for his high school crush for years, a young man puts up his best efforts to move out of the friend zone until she reveals she's getting married.
Learning of a fortune in gold being secretly shipped to Romania, master thieves Charlie and Riya assemble a crack team to steal it.
Desperate to keep her husband’s secret, a devoted politician’s wife struggles to stave off threats that could ruin their promising new life.
On the run from a dogged internal affairs agent, a corrupt cop reluctantly teams up with a defiant teen to unravel a conspiracy – before it's too late.
Years after they were childhood sweethearts, Manuela and Olmo share a night in Madrid, where they discuss their past and the possibility of a future.

Titulo: Stars in the Sky: A Hunting Story
Enredo: This documentary follows a group of hunters as they grapple with the complexities, controversies, and contradictions of pursuing animals in the wild.
In the wake of the plane crash that claimed the lives of 71 people, the Brazilian soccer club Chapecoense seeks to rebuild the team that made history.

Titulo: Blanche Gardin: I Talk to Myself

Enredo: When a long list of shenanigans lands Tyler in hot water, he’s forced to suit up and spend his summer training for an elite junior lifeguard program.
As summer returns to Malibu, Team Flounder takes to the beach to host — and unexpectedly compete in — the International Beachmaster Competition.
While visiting her fiancé's mother in southern Italy, a woman must fight the mysterious and malevolent curse intent on claiming her daughter.
A widowed, single mom takes a job caring for a young girl with spina bifida, and the two discover they have more in common than they realized.
Thrust from a violent home into a brutal custody center, a teenager learns to navigate a tough new reality and forge unlikely alliances to survive.

Titulo: Notes from Dunblane: Lessons from a School Shooting

Enredo: Heartbroken from her last relationship, an attorney is wary of falling in love again. But crossing paths with an ex upends her plans to finally move on.

Titulo: Elizabeth and Margaret: Love and Loyalty
Enredo: This documentary takes an intimate look at the complex, widely misunderstood relationship between Queen Elizabeth II and her sister, Princess Margaret.

Titulo: Lavell Crawford: Can a Brother Get Some Love?
Enredo: "Last Comic Standing" runner-up Lavell Crawford lords over a hometown crowd at St. Louis's Orpheum Theatre, raking in the love – and the laughs.

Titulo: Animals on the Loose: A You vs. Wild Movie
Enredo: When wild animals escape from a sanctuary, Bear Grylls — and you — must pursue them and secure their protective habitat. An interactive special.
A middle-aged boxer with a mixed record becomes a champion's sparring partner while dreaming of one last chance to end his career with a victory.

Titulo: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes: Maximum Overload

Enredo: When their parents' marriage threatens to crumble, the teenage Salazar siblings plot to reconcile them before their 20th wedding anniversary.
In this movie sequel to the hit series, Chuck returns home and talks to a reporter about life on the island with zany larva pals Red and Yellow.
Brazilian YouTube sensation Whindersson Nunes revisits his humble beginnings and much more in a series of playful stories and peculiar songs.
Inspired by Nobel Peace Prize winner Malala Yousafzai, a young girl defies the expectations of her father and village to pursue an education
Workaholic Will puts his humdrum life in LA on hold to fulfill his grandpa's last wish: visiting Mexico City's most iconic sights and falling in love.

Titulo: Sofía Niño de Rivera: Natural Selection

Enredo: This documentary offers an honest look at our fraught, complex relationship to video games from the perspectives of gamers and their concerned parents.
A beautiful, wealthy woman’s insatiable appetite for romance leads to tragedy and a police investigation.
Inspired by the movie "Thelma & Louise," three young people with Down syndrome leave the institution where they live to take a road trip together.
In Kuala Lumpur, an abused domestic worker tries to escape to Indonesia, while an idealistic cop insists on fighting corruption  – at a heavy price.
Fleeing the family business and an arranged marriage, Santa’s daughter chooses a magical adventure of her own: College.
In an occupied village, a teen girl is set to wed a stranger. But when she crosses over to meet her betrothed, her heart gets entangled at the border.
When he defies his cruel father and leaves New Caledonia to play rugby in France, young Soane learns hard lessons about life, love and success.
As the lives of rich and poor passengers aboard a steamship unfold, buried secrets, lustful affairs and selfish desires are exposed.
When caste discrimination prevents a villager from giving his deceased father a rightful burial, he takes his fight for equality to court.
A rookie lawyer with an emasculating past in baseball can break into the legal world only if he manages a law firm's ragtag company softball team.
Bank chairman Charles Bunbury – who knows next to nothing about banking – fights to save both his company and his marriage from disaster.
Exhausted with his mother’s failed attempts at setting him up with women, Ican hires an ideal partner from a matchmaking app.
After spending much of his adult life in New York, an affable economist returns home to Buenos Aires and tries to reconnect with his aloof father.
From his home on Maui, pioneering researcher, author and spiritual teacher Ram Dass reflects on love, life and death as his own days draw to a close.
In this dark comedy, a dysfunctional group of wannabe Basque terrorists awaits word about a new mission while Spain makes a run at the World Cup title.
Love came naturally for married couple Sonoko and Tetsuo. But his secret profession as a love doll designer clashes with her deeper, darker secret.
Johnnie To's character-centered drama follows a Hong Kong firefighting crew as they take on harrowing rescue missions and navigate personal dilemmas.
Amidst the bustle of a magnetic and multifaceted city, the budding love between two dreamers is tested.
When her son's condition becomes severe, a woman reconnects with the biological father. But the reunion puts a strain on their respective relationships.
When Lluís, a disinterested Spanish soldier, meets Carlana, he falls quickly in love, but soon discovers that Carlana's true passion is power.
Back in her childhood home to help her sister care for their comatose mother, Alicia must face a dark force from her past that now threatens her child.

Titulo: LEGO Marvel Spider-Man: Vexed By Venom

Enredo: This documentary about comedian Bill Hicks offers insight into his irreverent takes on, well, everything. Brother Steve Hicks is the star witness.
An all-around nice guy finds himself in a dangerous situation after he makes the ultimate sacrifice for the woman he loves in this drama.
A teenage equestrian and a local football player fall for each other, but simmering racism in their small town puts their relationship to the test.
A policeman's son overcomes his reluctance to join the force following a brutal attack on his father and ends up in the middle of a robbery case.
Childhood friends Abhay and Aaliya experience plenty of obstacles in their paths as they find their way in the world and back to each other.
Deadpan twin comics Keith and Kenny Lucas take the stage in Brooklyn with a set that touches on drugs, race, Deion Sanders, teachers and O.J. Simpson.
After moving to Australia, an American teen convinces her new friends to form a cheer squad and take on their biggest rivals in competition.
A devoted grandson’s mission to reunite his ailing grandmother with her ancestral home turns into a complicated, comic cross-border affair.
This offbeat comedy-drama follows six quirky newlywed couples as they set off on a bus from Mumbai to Goa on their honeymoons.
In this horror movie, a retired priest haunted by his sins is pulled back into the darkness when a friend begs him to help his possessed daughter.
The irrepressible Alonzo skewers Latino stereotypes, pricey luxuries and her mother's tough-love parenting in a night of sly and infectious comedy.
When a graduate student elopes with a plucky reporter, his wealthy, possessive mother connives with his militant brother-in-law to wreck the union.
A young man who gets tongue-tied around women writes a love letter to his crush, but it ends up in the hands of her mother, who thinks it's for her.
A street dog is taken in by a young couple, and the family pit becomes an instant accomplice as she adjusts to her new, loving home.
This documentary captures the joy and heartbreak of families separated by the U.S.-Mexico border sharing a short but bittersweet reunion in 2018.
Comedian Mo Gilligan blends smooth moves and sharp humor as he riffs on humble beginnings, family dynamics and the complex art of dancing in the club.
Short on sense but long on self-confidence, dotty Deliha sets her sights on a hunky photographer who opens up shop in her neighborhood.
When tragic events force an aspiring baseball player to forgo his big league dreams and return home, saving the family farm grants him renewed purpose.
While working at a family friend's business, a penniless orphan draws the attention of a corrupt competitor and is torn between divided loyalties.
When their college-age daughter suddenly begins acting erratically and is diagnosed with schizophrenia, a desperate couple seeks treatment for her.

Titulo: Dragons: Rescue Riders: Secrets of the Songwing
Enredo: When a musical dragon with a beautiful voice hypnotizes the dragons and people of Huttsgalor, the Rescue Riders have to find a way to break the spell.
In 1921 Barcelona, amid unrest between anarchists and the police, a cop plays both sides to learn who stole army weapons that could ignite a civil war.
Paco Ignacio Taibo II brings his book trilogy to life, highlighting Mexico's history in 1854-1867, a period he considers foundational to the country.
When her little sister claims she sees the dead, Alia consults a psychic, who opens her own eyes to the vengeful ghosts haunting their childhood home.
A lawyer is caught in a terrifying game of cat and mouse when a drink with an old friend escalates into an obsession that jeopardizes everyone she loves.
After her best friend dies, Barbs attempts to rediscover herself until love leaves her true identity — and heart — in question.
Follow the journey of Satnam Singh Bhamara as he works to fulfill his dream of becoming the first India-born player to be drafted into the NBA.
A sawmill owner and his teenage daughter become tangled in a deadly feud when a drug dealer stashes stolen cocaine on their remote property.
Members of the Thai idol girl group BNK48 open up about their experiences beyond the spotlight, their training and the nature of fame.
When his son is diagnosed with sickle cell disease, a man and his family struggle to face a new reality as they rediscover their shared love.
When a zealous gang leader plans to take out a friend-turned-rival for control of his turf, internal tensions complicate the battle to be the boss.
Sent undercover to investigate suspicious activity among a group of college students, a police officer gets more invested in his role than expected.

Titulo: Emicida: AmarElo – Live in São Paulo

Enredo: A young boy from Johannesburg arrives in KwaZulu-Natal and begins to read letters for villagers — then falls in love with one of the recipients.
After receiving a heart transplant from a murdered man, a cop is followed around by the victim’s ghost, who won’t rest until his death has been avenged.
After being dumped on New Year's Eve, Bill pursues his ex-girlfriend to an off-season Gulf Coast beach town, but things get complicated along the way.
Struggling in a loveless marriage, a hard-drinking, workaholic cop finds a chance at redemption after a fateful incident leaves him wounded.
In 1980s Hong Kong, a school principal forms a baseball team with an eclectic crew of local students who soon fight their way to the top of the league.
Seth Rogen and friends combine stand-up, sketches and music for an outrageous comedy special that could only come from the mind of Seth.
Mourning their father's death, a dysfunctional trio of siblings must face selling their beloved childhood beach house — and dealing with each other.
After getting fired, a police officer connects with a prostitute he met on the job in a red-light district and sets out to keep her off the streets.
Three gay siblings are told by their terminally ill father that they must each produce a grandchild in order to inherit their share of his fortune.
Threatened by creditors, a newly unemployed man agrees to work for a debt collector, but soon discovers his deal with the devil has unexpected costs.

When young Mukhsin arrives in a new town, 10-year-old tomboy Orked adopts him as her new best friend, and the two develop a touching friendship that begins to spill over into the inklings of first love.
When a pair of friends uncover a weed Bible, their magical stash gets stolen, sending them on a pot-fueled quest through Atlanta to find it.
It's Grabbleapple harvest season in the Rainbow Kingdom ... but Glummy Glooma doesn't want autumn to come. Can True and her friends save the festival?
When a man discovers he will be the father to a boy, his fear and insecurities send him on an emotional, humorous quest for his own manhood.
The loss of a child plunges Sade into a suicidal depression, but her suffering leads to faith – with a little assist from modern technology.
A young warrior and her familiar search for the sacred place said to fulfill wishes. It's best not to anger the ancient guardians and spirits.
After landing a job working for her longtime crush, an optimistic woman realizes that the man of her dreams isn't exactly who she envisioned.
A curious reporter finds love while pursuing the story of a mysterious figure who's leaving bags of cash for strangers around New York City.
This pawesome documentary explores how our feline friends became online icons, from the earliest text memes to the rise of celebrity cat influencers.

Titulo: Offline: Are You Ready for the Next Level?

Enredo: An unemployed Bollywood session violinist in Mumbai finally lands a small gig, but it's what happens on his way home that proves truly transformative.
Standup comedian Tim Allen delivers a set dedicated to "men stuff" like lawn care, power tools and why he grunts like an animal.

Titulo: My Little Pony: Equestria Girls - Rollercoaster of Friendship

Enredo: Against the backdrop of Nigeria's looming independence from Britain, detective Danladi Waziri races to capture a killer terrorizing local women.
Best friends Léa and Camille explore the notion of healing while traveling to Latin America in search of a cure for a terminal disease.
After becoming separated from her family, a young girl finds herself in the care of a heartbroken woman who faces her own struggles.
Forced to wed his childhood friend, a man obsessed with football attempts to get rid of his wife in order to keep the woman he truly loves.
Haunted by terrifying visions, a Muslim healer finds his faith tested when he helps a woman locked in battle, body and soul, with a diabolical leader.

Titulo: The Last Days of American Crime
Enredo: A bank robber joins a plot to commit one final, historic heist before the government turns on a mind-altering signal that will end all criminal behavior.
In 1895 Mumbai, spirited Indian lad Shiv Talpade defies British rule and sparse funding – and physics – to build the world's first airplane.
A mother uses her deceased daughter’s doll as a medium to communicate with her, but the consequences are chilling. The second of the “Doll” films.

Titulo: JFK: The Making of a President
Enredo: Explore how John F. Kennedy's worldview was influenced by his younger years, when he endured poor health, family tragedy and a demanding father.

Titulo: All the Freckles in the World
Enredo: Thirteen-year-old José Miguel is immune to 1994 World Cup fever until he realizes soccer is the only way to win the heart of his crush.
In early 1990s Malaysia, a Tamilian boy faces pressure from his immigrant father to focus on school but is drawn to his uncles’ lives of crime.
In this evocative documentary, an undocumented immigrant plans to return to Mexico after 16 years but his family tells him he needs to stay in the US.
A struggling music student discovers and tries to complete an unfinished symphony begun by a famous composer, whose career was ended by a past trauma.
In a raw stand-up comedy special, Mike Epps mixes it up as he tackles sexual misconduct, special ed, aging body parts and much more.
When its special ops agency is wiped out, Spain hastily assembles a new team to defuse a terrorist plot. But who are these scrappy would-be heroes?
Determined to marry before she turns 30, a woman tries to change her impulsive ways and do whatever it takes to win back the boyfriend who left her.
D.L. Hughley riffs on hot-button political issues, celebrity scandals, his mother's tough love and more in a rapid-fire stand-up show in Philadelphia.
In this special live event, giants of stand-up come together to commemorate the 25th anniversary of Russell Simmons's groundbreaking "Def Comedy Jam."
Mexico City restaurant star Gabriela Cámara opens sister eatery Cala in San Francisco, with a similar menu and unusually welcoming kitchen culture.
Wealthy and spoiled, a young man finds something to fight for when he falls in love with an environmental activist protesting his family's business.
A cooly confident aging hit man returns from exile in Paris to his old city, Mumbai, to revisit his past and perform one last job.
Aspiring teen thieves learn what it takes to be successful pickpockets on the streets of Bogotá from a master in the arts of trickery and deception.
Benjie Nycum travels to Wyoming to visit his ex-lover, Michael Glatze, a former gay activist who now lives with his wife and works as a church pastor.
After their child was abducted and murdered, John and Reve Walsh fought to raise national awareness of the problem of missing children.
In this live-action adventure, the gang heads to Hawaii, where Timmy learns the source of all fairy magic is in dangerous hands.
To claim a big inheritance, a down-on-his-luck mechanic must win a series of competitions as outlined in his birth father's will.
A young chauffeur who's at a crossroads in his life escorts a pair of clients around Barcelona and becomes embroiled in their mysterious quest.

Titulo: ReMastered: Who Killed Jam Master Jay?
Enredo: Run-DMC DJ Jam Master Jay made a huge impact in music and his community. But friends and family still seek closure years after his unsolved murder.
When Japanese troops invade Hong Kong, young Benny Ho flees to Macau and rises to the top of the city's casino business with pluck, diligence and wit.
In this all-access pass, IndyCar champion Scott Dixon and his team navigate the risks on the road in the quest to win it all.
Kidnapped by guerrillas in Beirut, a French photojournalist refuses to yield his dignity despite being tortured and brainwashed by his captors.
After a woman is very publicly left at the altar, the PR expert hired to fix the situation winds up falling in love with her.
A suicidal war veteran finds like-minded souls in a surf therapy program that helps traumatized soldiers heal while riding the waves.
A Google executive boldly attempts a death-defying mission to travel to space and free-fall back to Earth without a rocket.
To clear his criminal record, an ex-special forces soldier agrees to lead a team to retrieve a double-crossing mercenary and deliver him to justice.
Up against a corrupt government official and crushing poverty, a young boy in the Delhi slums attempts to raise funds to build himself his own toilet.
An undercover cop finds himself in a strange position after infiltrating a "gang" that pulls wildly popular pranks on corrupt officials in Mumbai.
Brilliant young students discover a breakthrough that could change humankind, but soon find themselves the subjects of a much bigger experiment.
In a rollicking special, Thiago Ventura jokes about life in the hood, social issues and more, explaining how actions speak louder than words.
Amid growing tensions in their marriage, a Johannesburg professor and his journalist wife find their lives upended by a famous, hard-partying author.
In rural Pennsylvania, a working-class single mom must pick up the pieces and step up to raise her grandson after her daughter suddenly disappears.
A young dysfunctional couple tries to patch up their relationship through sessions with a highly unconventional therapist.
Raised in the privileged bubble of Delhi's elite, a teen is compelled to question his outlook on life and love when his older brother comes out as gay.
Rising from disadvantage to become a state leader, a tenacious politician learns that with great power comes great responsibility, ruthlessness and risk.
When Santa crash-lands in the junkyard on Christmas Eve, Hank, Trash Truck and their animal friends all have a hand in rescuing the holiday for everyone.
Homicide detective Gene Handsome sets out to solve a woman's murder while searching for clues about what's missing from his personal life.

Titulo: Hope Frozen: A Quest to Live Twice
Enredo: A Thai scientist and his family decide to cryonically freeze their cherished, dying toddler. This heartfelt documentary follows their journey.
When a small town's letters to Santa accidentally go up in smoke, two elves venture out of the North Pole to retrieve every missing wish.
The extraordinary life of beloved acting teacher and theatre producer Wynn Handman is recalled in this portrait of a provocative, innovative artist.
After growing up in a tumultuous household, Yura finds herself in a love triangle with two close friends as she faces a personal and financial crisis.
A college student seizes his chance with a crush when an unexpected encounter turns into a night of bold dares, deep confessions and possible romance.
Four man-children in an elite tactical unit gallivant around Macau for a weekend of debauchery that gets them in trouble with the law.
A resilient housewife, her husband and their marriage therapist become mired in a toxic love triangle and a plot to obtain an antique manuscript.
Comic sensation Amy Schumer riffs on sex, dating and the absurdities of fame in a bold and uncensored stand-up set at Denver's Bellco Theater.
When a fit of anger leads to a serious injury, a sidelined soccer star returns to his hometown and reluctantly agrees to train the local youth.
Three cheating husbands end up paying the price for their infidelities when their spouses hire a private detective – who falls for one of the wives.
A realtor and her daughter get taken captive by two fugitive criminals during an open house, forcing her to find creative ways to ensure their survival.
The discovery of the tomb of William Tell’s son in a town in the Basque Country spurs the village's cantankerous citizens to lobby for Swiss annexation.
After living in America for years, a teenage girl moves back to the Netherlands and is quickly singled out as a misfit by the popular clique at school.
Brazilian comedian Afonso Padilha dives into his humble beginnings and digs out hilarious stories about his childhood in this very personal set.
After a pregnant woman is murdered, her spirit seeks revenge against her increasingly terrified killers, who are determined to finish her off for good.
Fourteen years after the woman he loved left him, a married man ventures to Amsterdam to find her but must decide where his heart lies.
A young boy, upset by his parents' divorce, becomes infatuated with his grandmother's neighbor, an entrancing dancer he watches through a window.
An elderly woman finds her life disrupted when her family and village realize she has a chance at a world record for being the oldest grandmother alive.
A gifted young singer becomes an instant sensation on a popular talent show. But her real goal is earning the love of her father, a member of the jury.

Titulo: Dragons: Rescue Riders: Hunt for the Golden Dragon
Enredo: It's the treasure hunt of a lifetime for the Rescue Riders, who must race to find a precious golden dragon egg and protect it from evil pirates.

Titulo: The Last Kids on Earth: Happy Apocalypse to You
Enredo: Help Jack and his monster-battling friends make choices to stay alive — and have some fun — in this interactive "Last Kids on Earth" adventure!
Finding himself in a desperate situation, undercover agent Emman asks his former best friend, Erika, to join him on a dangerous mission.
On India's Independence Day, a zany mishap in a Mumbai chawl disrupts a young love story while compelling the residents to unite in aid of a little boy.
Years after his teen romance with Milea, a now-adult Dilan tells his version of their love story when a high school reunion brings them back together.
When his former partners vote to sell off a pricey piece of stolen jewelry, a thief recruits his grandson to help him retain it and repent for his deed.
After falling for Geez, a heartthrob at school, Ann must confront family opposition, heartache and deception as their romance struggles.
With her home devastated by war, a Lebanese poet takes a cross-country road trip, looking for glimmers of hope through nostalgic memories and verse.
Former con artist Sanju surrounds himself with the finer things, a blissful life troubled by only one thing: his wife, who wants even more.
A sound engineer falls for a model but after an unfortunate accident, he fights to save their love by triggering her senses.
A cop full of self-doubt loses his gun five days before he's due to leave the force, and becomes an unexpected hero as he tries to retrieve it.
A former actress takes a trip to Japan, where she meets a young man who provides an escape from reality and makes her consider a different way of life.
When three different boys propose to a lively, strictly reared girl who yearns to be a performer, she agrees to marry the winner of a singing contest.
After his wife dies in a car accident, a grief-stricken man visits his estranged mother-in-law in Maine, where they try to help each other heal.
Just as Simone works up the courage to tell her conservative Jewish family she's a lesbian, she finds herself attracted to a male Senegalese chef.
Lawmakers and activists with conflicting ideologies speak about the complexities of Catalonia's politics and the fight for its independence from Spain.
Felix Lobrecht aims his dark humor at overly polite culture, weird laughter, the sheer awkwardness of a walking baby and more in this stand-up special.
Class divides become thorns in the budding romance between the crony of a nativist Mumbai politician and the new, North Indian resident of his chawl.
Through rare interviews, images and wiretap audio, this documentary reconstructs the last nine years of Colombian drug lord Pablo Escobar's life.
When a major drug deal goes sour, the queen of the Warsaw underworld must contend with a rival criminal, a crossed ally and a religious fighter.
Fearing rejection, a young man struggles to declare his feelings for his best friend, who soon falls for another man — until a fateful incident.
In the age of Buddha and his philosophy of nonviolence, a warmonger king plots the destruction of an enemy kingdom to rescue the woman he loves.
Framed by a politician for committing murder, a lower-class boy hires the only counsel he can afford: a lawyer with no courtroom experience.
When a young man becomes possessed after playing a Ouija game, a ghost hunter investigates the evil spirit dwelling within him.
Garfield has long been the champ at a yearly competition for the funniest comic strip. But this time, Garfield must battle tall, handsome Ramone.
Determined to bring traditional bhangra to the world stage, a dancer preps for an international competition against a rival with dreams of her own.
When a dispute breaks out between five siblings over their mother’s property, one devoted son will go to any lengths to protect her land.
A man foils an attempted murder, then flees the crew of would-be killers along with their intended target as a woman he's just met tries to find him.
Yearning for a better life, a single mother with a passion for cooking gets a shot at greatness when her son enters her into a top reality cooking show.
Hoping to do good while making millions, three college graduates create a startup. But as business begins to flourish, their own bond starts to fray.
When his newlywed wife becomes disenchanted because he failed to protect her from danger, Omar seeks the help of a quirky psychiatrist to win her back.
Having driven away many of his employees, Bossman and three of his long-suffering workers try to find cheap labor in Vietnam but find trouble instead.
Three men are stunned to find their faces on a poster promoting vasectomies, and must prove to their upset loved ones that they're innocent victims.

Titulo: Madness in the Desert: The Paris to Dakar Story

Enredo: Coping with heartbreak, the shy owner of a floundering cafe finds solace in the Javanese love songs of Didi Kempot.
Now a lecturer in Edinburgh, Fahri tries to begin a new chapter as the love of his life, Aisha, volunteers in the Gaza Strip. Have they moved on?
Two buddies working dead-end cashier jobs endure a mind-blowing series of events on their quest to get to the hip-hop show of their lives.
Under pressure to marry, a perennial bachelor hires a much younger woman to act as his fiancée, but her bond with his family throws his plan for a loop.
Mistreated by his cruel uncle, an imaginative orphan with autism sees hope when a fairy vows to change his life with a week of enchanted recipes.
Wyatt Cenac heads to Brooklyn to share his observations on the borough that's the backdrop for three sitcoms and a reality show about cheesemongers.
A teen ballerina discovers hip-hop by chance and is faced with an impossible choice: Does she follow her parents’ footsteps... or her newfound passion?
Reunited in their hometown for their father's funeral, two self-interested brothers meet a peculiar woman who shares a huge secret about their family.
To upgrade his life, a simple man fakes his credentials as a lawyer when sudden extraordinary abilities give him the talent to thrive.
Two brothers — one a narcotics agent and the other a general — finally discover the identity of the drug lord who murdered their parents decades ago.

Titulo: The Road to El Camino: Behind the Scenes of El Camino: A Breaking Bad Movie
Enredo: Aaron Paul, Vince Gilligan and other cast members, producers and crew share stories and footage from the making of "El Camino."
During the internet's infancy, a vulnerable woman follows her sister into the sex industry as a webcam model but her sudden popularity tests their bond.
After knocking a celebrity unconscious before a huge job, a bumbling pack of pals tries to avoid a lawsuit by replacing her with a look-alike.
It's up to True and her friends to save the day when a hungry Yeti sneaks a forbidden treat and fills the kingdom with Howling Greenies.
Bo thinks her holiday gift-giving isn't good enough, so she heads north to study under Santa Claus – only to find he's missing.
Lee Su-geun's rise to Korean comedy stardom went hand in hand with his mastery over picking up social cues. Now, he's ready to share his know-hows.
When his partner in crime goes missing, a small-time crook’s life is transformed as he dedicates himself to raising the daughter his friend left behind.
Stand-up comedian Urzila Carlson keeps the crowd roaring with her thoughts on recasting "The Biggest Loser," sex tape regrets and boxed wine hangovers.
Comic Sam Kinison lets it rip with this performance at L.A.'s Wiltern theatre, skewering every segment of modern society from religion to television.
When pretty new neighbor Seema falls for their shy roommate Sid, jealous womanizers Omi and Jai plot to break up the new lovebirds.
A young man falls for a heroic general and soon follows her footsteps as humans defend Earth against extraterrestrials seeking a precious energy source.
Aiming for fame, a struggling singer finds his long-lost millionaire twin and falls for his brother's secretary as a plot brews to steal the fortune.
This powerful Tamil action film follows the shared fate of two very different siblings: policeman Thiru and his roguish brother, Guru.
Asian American creatives pay passionate tribute to the iconic, stereotype-busting "Baby-Sitters Club" character in this heartfelt documentary short.

Titulo: Chris Rock Total Blackout: The Tamborine Extended Cut
Enredo: In this extended cut of his 2018 special, Chris Rock takes the stage for a special filled with searing observations on fatherhood, infidelity and politics.
Talented sugar artists compete for $10,000 over two rounds of competition — candy and sugar sculpture — in this "Sugar Rush" spinoff special.

Titulo: Los Tigres del Norte at Folsom Prison
Enredo: The beloved norteño band Los Tigres del Norte performs for the inmates of Folsom Prison on the 50th anniversary of Johnny Cash's iconic concert.
M'Dear and her sisters struggle to keep their singing act together before a church Christmas pageant while Grandpa teaches the kids a valuable lesson.
Reeling from a broken heart and career meltdown, a singer takes a gig at a swanky island resort — where her ex-fiancé happens to be getting married.

Titulo: Larry The Cable Guy: Remain Seated

Enredo: In rural India, a child with hydrocephalus gets a chance at life-changing surgery after her photos go viral. This documentary charts her journey.
When three adult siblings meet the offbeat man who their widowed mom fawns over, they take drastic actions to stop them from ever getting married.
A martial arts specialist accidentally becomes a superhero when he steps in – in costume – to help the cops catch a criminal.
When the patriarch of an emigrant Nigerian family visits their female-led Canadian home, traditional values collide with newer ones.
An ad creative and a successful exec have a great marriage — until he wants to be a dad just as her star is rising. Then he brings someone new home.

Titulo: I Love You - A Divorce Comedy
Todo lo que sería Lucas Lauriente
Enredo: In his stand-up set, Argentine comic Lucas Lauriente animatedly rattles off reflections on different generations and begs kids to stop saying "goals."

Titulo: The Day I Lost My Shadow

Enredo: An off-color joke nearly cost him everything. Brazilian comic Rafinha Bastos talks about that and much more, from his divorce to finding love again.
When Omar's grandfather forces him to get a job at a tech company in Mexico City, he meets a quirky ensemble of nine-to-fivers ... and some nemeses.
Torn between his past and present girlfriends, a confused bachelor’s indecisiveness spins a web of lies and cheating as he struggles to commit.
When her son comes out to her as gay, a religious mother struggles to reconcile his truth with her own beliefs and their orthodox family values.
The owner of a struggling carnival starts putting on small-time shows to save his wonderland as an old friend asks for help with a magical mission.
Comedian Vir Das tackles nationalism, globalism, good food and bad politics in two cleverly crosscut performances in New York and New Delhi.
When his mother suffers a traumatic incident, a boy from the Mumbai slums treks to Delhi to deliver his written plea for justice to the Prime Minister.
While chasing her dream of becoming a chef, Zeliha cooks up trouble in the kitchen with her wild, kooky and unsuspecting ways.
The lives of five hapless, petty criminals careen into madcap disarray when their plan to abduct a wealthy minister’s son goes horribly wrong.
A trio of filmmakers treks across India to explore the correlation between vanishing rivers, massive energy projects and renewable energy sources.

Titulo: Vir Das: Outside in - The Lockdown Special

Enredo: A desperate man attempts to burglarize the home of a wealthy woman, but finds himself face-to-face with a crew of armed robbers who have the same idea.
Villains are rampaging through Charter City and the Flex Fighters – Jake, Ricardo and Nathan – need your help to halt the chaos.
In this stand-up special, comedian Hazel Brugger offers her breezy takes on unruly geese, chatty gynecologists, German bank loans and more.
After a purification ritual unravels, a conflicted Taoist priest attempts to help a lonely young psychic whose aunt is possessed by a powerful demon.

Titulo: Amandla! A Revolution in Four-Part Harmony

Enredo: Journalist Naresh is hired to probe illegal activities on an island. When he's captured, a fellow prisoner gives him a ring with magic powers.
In Naples, Buenos Aires and New York, people reflect on the Neapolitan tradition of "suspended coffee" and how it changed their lives.
An ambitious entertainment lawyer tries to sign a singing sensation in his sister's small town, but a local soon captures his attention — and heart.

Titulo: The Massively Mixed-Up Middle School Mystery
Enredo: After the school principal gets pranked, a curious crew of preteen super sleuths tests their detective skills to solve an underwater ruse.
Two close childhood friends take drastically different paths in life, but meet by chance years later and fall in love, unaware of their past bond.
On the night his ex-lover mysteriously dies, a top fashion designer has a serious accident, raising questions on whether the incidents are linked.
Two half siblings separated by family conflict cross paths as adults at a fashion agency – but one of them has a vendetta, unbeknownst to the other.
An elite international squad of uniquely skilled special forces is assembled to combat a rising underground terrorist threat in the Middle East.
When a storm terrorizes his patch, a pumpkin cast out for his shape must step up to use his smarts to save the day – and to prove himself.
When a cabbie chances upon his childhood sweetheart, he tries to rekindle old feelings but finds that mature love is a more complicated matter.

Titulo: Story of Kale: When Someone's in Love
Enredo: After leaving a toxic relationship, Dinda embarks on a romance with Kale, whose view on love soon shatters as he wrestles with his own insecurities.
A fisherman returns home after a three-year absence only to find the woman he loves drifting away, the sailors feuding and his community unraveling.
Home for the holidays, a broke puppeteer knows there’s treasure buried somewhere under her town. To find it, all she has to do is die – almost.
Four small-town French teens who style themselves after American rappers set out to avenge a classroom insult and end up on a mind-blowing adventure.
A chance encounter soon intertwines the lives of a reserved businessman and a vibrant photographer who is living with a grave heart condition.
Undercover cameras expose public floggings, executions and other brutality in Saudi Arabia, and introduce those risking their own lives for change.

Titulo: Willy and the Guardians of the Lake

Enredo: To better himself, a spoiled prince temporarily assumes a commoner’s identity. But he soon learns his palace has been gifted to his father’s new wife.
After a sex video subjects her friend to mockery and bullying, a transfer student sets out to reveal the truth as campus secrets come to light.
Madly in love with a brilliant scientist studying an immunizing protein produced by penguins, a timid med student offers her body to his research.
After trying to live in the "real world" and concluding it isn't for him, Garfield must return to his comic-strip home before getting trapped forever.

Titulo: El club de los buenos infieles
Enredo: Four childhood buddies in passionless marriages try a counterintuitive idea: a secret club for men who want to cheat – to regain lust for their wives.

Titulo: Felipe Esparza: They're Not Gonna Laugh At You

Enredo: Examine how the group of alternative hip-hop artists known as the Good Lifers started a movement and created a robust, progressive musical community.
Now parents, Omar and Salma hit some obstacles while raising their two children and staying in love after the honeymoon ends.
While investigating a bank robbery, a squad of overweight police officers undergoes rigorous training to shed pounds.
With only her mother's diary and a locket as clues, a South African woman travels to Paris in search of the long-lost sibling she never knew she had.
A luxury hotel chauffeur's life is turned upside down when he unexpectedly becomes the focus of a renowned painter's final art project.
In an ancient sport traditionally reserved for men, 20-year-old female sumo prodigy Hiyori attempts to revolutionize Japan’s national pastime.

Titulo: Ma Rainey's Black Bottom: A Legacy Brought to Screen
Enredo: Viola Davis, Denzel Washington, George C. Wolfe and more share the heart, soul and history that brought August Wilson’s timeless play to the screen.
Over the course of one memorable and adventure-filled year, Felix Starck documents his 18,000-kilometer bicycle journey across 22 countries.
When a self-help writer's advice goes wrong, she finds herself in the crosshairs of an obsessive young woman with a thirst for vengeance.
An astute but old-fashioned law clerk steps up to help the owner of a cafe in a legal battle that has both business and personal ramifications.

Titulo: A Triumph of the Heart: The Ricky Bell Story

Enredo: In this 2014 standup special filmed in San Francisco, comedic genius D.L. Hughley entertains with his hilarious take on current affairs and more.
As three young professionals chase their wildly different dreams, their relationships with each other indelibly impact their journeys of self-discovery.
After falling in love during college, architect Maddy and free spirit Payal have five wonderful years together, until a mystery suddenly divides them.
After a long stint in the army, an ex-lieutenant returns home and enters an underground MMA match to take on a local mobster and protect his family.
A group of uber-popular, social media influencers’ trip to a digital media festival grows dark when an evil spirit wants to lure them to their demise.
During a wilderness getaway, a gang of sociopathic criminals kidnap a woman and assault her husband, who must summon all his strength to save her.

Titulo: The Spooky Tale of Captain Underpants Hack-a-ween
Enredo: When Melvin tries to cancel Halloween, clever best friends Harold and George create their own spooky holiday – and it's a huge success!
Mentored by an enigmatic tycoon, an ambitious young man faces a crisis when his rise in power draws him deep into the occult.
Sick of keeping their love a secret from their constantly bickering mothers, a young couple seeks to uncover the cause of the women’s longstanding war.
Jimo, an outcast who can see monsters, teams up with a monster hunter to fight evil forces and soon discovers her greater calling.
An Argentine comedian espouses the values of feminism, speaking on topics like sex, language, abortion and why it's OK to let a man buy you dinner.
From Casino du Liban, Lebanese actor and comedian Adel Karam delivers earthy punchlines on kissing norms, colonoscopies and a porn star named Rocco.
Go backstage with French rap duo Bigflo & Oli in this intimate music documentary, then join the superstar siblings as they embark on a major tour.
When a middle-aged filmmaker meets an alluring stranger at a party, he's haunted by troubling memories of his past relationships.
A young reporter's investigation into a string of grisly suicides takes a dangerous detour when she follows the clues to a cursed stretch of road.
As a son deals with his own struggles, he must calm his father's obsession with fishing before his outlandish behavior ruins the entire family.

Titulo: Alejandro Sanz: What I Was Is What I Am
Enredo: A retrospective look at the life and career of Grammy-award winning Spanish musician Alejandro Sanz.
Looking for a way out of his impoverished life, a lowly hotel waiter joins an underground fight club. Then he needs a way out of that.
A free-spirited couple leave the city to retire in the country. But when they're swindled by a relative, life in the countryside loses its luster.

Titulo: Super Monsters: Once Upon a Rhyme
Enredo: From Goldilocks to Hansel and Gretel, the Super Monsters reimagine classic fairy tales and favorite nursery rhymes with a musical, magical spin!
The U.S. Navy Seal team tackles a top-secret mission at a research center where scientists have mysteriously disappeared and another life form awaits.

Titulo: Spirit Riding Free: Spirit of Christmas
Enredo: Lucky and friends must figure out how to get home in time for Christmas when a falling boulder – and a serious snowstorm – derail their travel plans.
Determined to win the heart of his childhood crush from orphanage, EJ becomes a boxer with superpowers and soon confronts a formidable villain.
A disillusioned security guard transforms into a masquerade, channeling ancestral spirits as he roams the streets of Lagos.
Tormented by bullies, an aspiring drag star working at an Alaskan cannery becomes a skilled fighter and is tapped for competition by a boxing coach.
Things get spooky when Bheem and his buddies travel to the border of Dholakpur, known for its eerie history and rumored to be haunted.
Tensions rise and untold secrets surface for three royal sisters when a family treasure is stolen the night before an antique auction.

Titulo: Rob Schneider: Asian Momma, Mexican Kids
Enredo: Former "Saturday Night Live" star Rob Schneider returns to the stage and shares his take on life, love and dinosaur dreams in this stand-up special.
In this documentary, South African rapper Nasty C hits the stage and streets of Tokyo, introducing himself to the city's sights, sounds and culture.
One football match on a dirt pitch near Rome becomes a day of reckoning as a young player, his coach and their team's owner wrestle internal demons.
When aspiring fashion designer Andi reconnects with her ex-boyfriend Max, she's surprised to learn that he's in a relationship with a man.
When a teenager discovers he's not really human, he ventures out to a remote island to explore his roots and confronts a series of wild challenges.
When his brother becomes involved in a deadly bank robbery, a heartbroken cop vows to track down and retrieve his wayward sibling – dead or alive.
Armed with sly wit, a fresh outlook and plenty of style, French comedy star Fary veers from dating to stereotypes and beyond in this exclusive special.
As her own wedding looms on the horizon, a marriage counselor strives to save her future in-laws' crumbling relationship.

Titulo: The Misadventures of Hedi and Cokeman
Enredo: In Paris, two dysfunctional dealers use family ties to try to boost their small drug business in this crass comedy based on the webseries.
Filmed in front of a raucous crowd, comedian Ralphie May unleashes his hilariously raunchy perspective in his first Netflix original stand-up special.
A spirited but naive young woman seeks a one-night stand, but after discovering her date’s real identity, things quickly go from casual to complicated.
Emergency room doctor Javid Abdelmoneim endeavors to learn the truth about alcohol, both its benefits and risks, by exploring the science of drinking.
Fresh from a tour, comedian Katherine Ryan shares shrewd observations about school bullies, revenge bodies and raising a very fancy child.
Arab-American comedian Mo Amer recounts his life as a refugee comic, from traveling with the name Mohammed to his long path to citizenship.
A wedding in a Malaysian village leaves out one guest: a scorned vampire ghost bent on settling a secret score with the groom and anyone in her way.
In an abandoned hospital in Tainan, visitors seeking to communicate with their relatives' spirits are haunted by disturbing, supernatural occurrences.
After reckless teens kill an Amish child, a prosecutor attempts to bring the youths to justice despite the condemnation he faces from the community.
A scoundrel's mission to escape his family and remarry on Mars is hilariously scrubbed when a mishap with a black hole turns his son into an old man.
When a beloved secret agent falls deep into a coma, his bumbling brother must defend their community from a divisive political threat.
Country music star Brad Paisley hosts a night of music and laughs with comics Nate Bargatze, John Heffron, Jon Reep, Sarah Tiana and Mike E. Winfield.
In a tailspin after her marriage collapses, Jamie falls for a helpful gentleman whose interest in her welfare hides sinister motives.
A seasoned couples therapist comes to realize she might need help with her own marriage after meeting a new pair of young clients.
An immigration lawyer and a Nigerian woman caught in a ring of corruption team up to uncover the truth behind a suspicious death in a detention center.
Bodybuilders come together from around the world to compete in the Mr. Olympia competition and try to achieve their goals of physical perfection.
A disenchanted chef tries to help her parents restore their failing hotel but cooks up feelings for an investor with his sights set on the property.
In three interwoven stories, love ends up in limbo as romantic partners navigate bliss, loss, failures and feelings while trying to make happiness last.
In a town infamous for female infanticide, a young woman’s arrival has local bachelors vying for her hand in marriage — but she has a bigger agenda.
Close quarters and new romances add trouble to the rocky relationship between a high-strung young woman and her demanding mother.

Titulo: Bridget Christie: Stand Up For Her

Enredo: What is anime? Through deep-dives with notable masterminds of this electrifying genre, this fast-paced peek behind the curtain seeks to find the answers.
In this documentary short, a diverse group of men and women discuss their personal journeys as they prepare for the U.S. citizenship test.
When a restaurant owner in Cyprus returns to Beijing to sign divorce papers, a drunk woman he encounters triggers a string of mishaps.

Titulo: Octonauts and the Caves of Sac Actun
Mission Kathmandu: The Adventures of Nelly & Simon
Rogue Warfare: Death of a Nation
Enredo: As their leader recovers from trauma, a global team of elite soldiers must regroup and stop the deadly plans of an extremist mastermind within 36 hours.
When a novelist seeks inspiration by urging his wife to have an affair, the line between his story and his real life grows disconcertingly blurry.
After their 99th breakup, a career woman and her carefree partner open a cafe where customers can put up souvenirs of past relationships.
South African comedian Loyiso Gola serves up filter-free humor as he riffs about race, identity, politics, and a school prank gone embarrassingly wrong!
Mind games and mystery abound as a detective investigates the disappearance of a woman’s body from a morgue in this Hindi remake of a Spanish thriller.
In three stories set in Northeast India, a child goes on the run, a young adult falls in with the wrong crowd and a desperate man turns to crime.
A dejected small-town music teacher grapples with guilt and regret when his ex-pupil who once loved him returns home as the star he always wanted to be.
While she successfully advocates for her female clients in difficult divorce cases, a lawyer’s trauma from sexual assault impacts her own marriage.
In 1976 Beirut, after a rendezvous with her old flame, soon-to-wed Noha witnesses a violent incident and changes course on a path to self-realization.
In Lagos, a journalist goes undercover as a prostitute to expose human trafficking. What she finds is a world of exploited women and ruthless violence.
When a man outgrows a childhood friendship and commits to marrying his girlfriend, obsession and spiritual warfare soon disrupt his peaceful life.
Convinced only a miracle can save them from failing school exams, a trio of friends seek help from a magician. To their surprise, he gamely complies.
True and Bartleby try to cheer up the Rainbow Kingdom’s loneliest citizen, but his gloomy mood is contagious! Can a trio of wishes turn things around?
Teen witch Bibi and horse-loving Tina face trouble when a posh girl flirts with Tina's boyfriend and a crook sets his greedy eyes on a promising foal.
A pampered but kind-hearted average joe ditches his romancing and peacekeeping ways when he’s framed for a murder he didn’t commit.
A production crew that thinks it's making a documentary about a humble Mumbai rickshaw driver unmasks a horrifying truth about their film's subject.
Three brothers – a gangster, a scholar and an impressionable teen – learn hard lessons in the gritty suburbs while searching for the means to survive.
Through the lens of faiths and cultures in seven provinces in Indonesia, this documentary follows individuals who strive to address climate change.
French comic Gad Elmaleh regales a Montreal crowd with tales of awkward mix-ups and baffling customs he's encountered since moving to the U.S.
Single at 34, Isoken is maneuvered by her mother toward a relationship with a black entrepreneur but finds herself drawn to a white photojournalist.
On the 200th anniversary of the Battle of Waterloo, thousands of enthusiasts reenact the epic clash. But there can only be one Napoleon.
As Sarah and her child look to settle in Jakarta, Zaenab searches for answers and gets caught between defending her marriage to Doel or letting it go.
Battling terminal cancer, a woman writes a one of a kind notebook about life, death and love for her son to remember her by. Based on a true story.

Titulo: Amelia: A Tale of Two Sisters
Enredo: Eight decades after her disappearance, Amelia Earhart's incredible accomplishments are still celebrated, thanks in large part to her sister Muriel.
Two strangers meet on a dating app and experience instant chemistry, but their relationship unravels as jarring differences catch up to them.
Seeking the formula behind a magical elixir bequeathed to him by his father, a veterinary professor gets embroiled in a mobster's horse-racing scheme.
Two days before their final exams, three teen girls make a seaside getaway to have the time of their lives.
Worlds collide when Henry makes plans to spend Saturday on the sofa watching a "Gross Class Zero" marathon — and his favorite characters come to life!

Titulo: Albert Pinto Ko Gussa Kyun Aata Hai?
Enredo: As the police investigate his disappearance, a young man heads to Goa to carry out an act of vengeance fueled by years of pent-up anger toward society.

Titulo: Jeff Garlin: Our Man in Chicago
El Potro, lo mejor del amor

Enredo: Four buddies attend a class taught by a love guru who leads them to question their romantic attachments — until her hidden agenda comes to light.
After a betrayal at work, a finance professional becomes an assistant to a bride shaman in order to salvage her only remaining property — and love life.

Titulo: In Defense of a Married Man
Enredo: A lawyer's husband is having an affair. When his mistress is found dead, he becomes the prime suspect – and his wife must take charge of his defense.
To avenge his master, a wine-loving young man steps up his fighting skills to defeat a powerful thief in a life-or-death match.
Following his best friend's death, Arci takes charge of her two boisterous children with some help from their gang-affiliated uncle.
In Delhi for the first time, a Mumbai girl loses her phone but gets a surprise chance at true love with a local boy who begrudgingly helps her.
Twins separated by a court order meet at camp and decide to reunite their parents, unaware of the dark secret that drove them apart years before.
When the Italian prime minister meets his lover and political rival while on an official trip to Budapest during Christmas week, things go topsy-turvy.
A brainy private school student is transferred to a far less elite institution, where he must fend off classmates who settle scores with fistfights.
Argentine comedian Sebastián Wainraich highlights the comedy in everyday life, from minibars to reasons why funerals are better than weddings.
Through interviews with locals, this documentary investigates the triggers and outcomes of the 2013 communal riots in the heart of Uttar Pradesh.
At midnight on his 10th birthday, a boy scours the lesser-known Kolkata streets in search of a father he’s never met, carrying a letter he can’t read.
Argentine comedian Agustín "Radagast" Aristarán adds doses of magic, music and acting to his high-energy stand-up routine.
New high school grad and avid gamer Cenk is recruited to an intense esports team that trains for a tournament with a life-changing prize.
When staff salaries get stolen at his school, a reluctant new teacher sets out to recoup the money and soon discovers the joys of teaching.

Titulo: George Lopez: We'll Do It for Half
Octonauts and the Great Barrier Reef

Enredo: Ayşe returns from Germany to her Black Sea hometown and sets out to fulfill her mom's dying wish — to care for her beloved bee farms.
Two kids and their pet dog (aka the Ghost Patrol) get a call about an old manor and soon find they are investigating their first real haunted house.
When his cruel uncle abandons him, a young orphan learns to access the untapped superpowers that have been waiting within him all along.
Bird watchers on both sides of the U.S.-Mexico border share their enthusiasm for protecting and preserving some of the world's most beautiful species.
As a killer stalks the streets, a troubled young courier suspects that a doctor may be the long-lost sister he hasn't seen since childhood.
When a town suffers an economic collapse, social unrest forces a family to seek refuge in the wilderness as bitter outlaws threaten their survival.
A young priest coaches a team of uncoordinated monks in order to win a soccer tournament and save their monastery from being turned into a hotel.
An asylum patient’s troubled past threatens his grasp on reality as fellow hospital residents begin disappearing at the hands of an unknown entity.
Jack Whitehall hits the stage with hilarious tales about happy couples, life in hotels, human stupidity and his well-traveled father.
Two young buddies seek love in Hawaii, and upon returning home in disappointment, soon entangle themselves in a messy identity swap.
A bright and promising young girl gets abducted and taken to a terrorist camp, where she unexpectedly crosses paths with her soulmate.
To escape conviction on criminal charges, a businessman agrees to aid a risky police mission, but his motives soon turn suspicious.
As they near their 25th wedding anniversary, Rick and Cristy try to conceal their crumbling marriage while their family prepares for a big celebration.
Standup comedian and "Daily Show" correspondent Gina Yashere delivers a sharp set of wry observations on the environment, money and more.
A young Basque man is radicalized in 1960s America after being forbidden from participating in a parade on racial grounds.
Luminous funnywoman Sommore wows Miami with her unique take on body modification, Internet sex, the world of celebrities and more.
Ahead of summer break, a couple heads to a seaside resort where intimate interactions with other villagers make for anything but a peaceful holiday.
In this sequel to the 2016 hit "The Wedding Party," a couple's date night ends in an accidental proposal, sparking a series of chaotic family events.
When an aging father seeks the help of a doctor and a journalist to look for the son who left him 16 years ago, he learns some surprising truths.
After a singing pup with big dreams of stardom gets dognapped and escapes with a friend's help, her journey home is a fun, music-filled adventure.
A high school teacher volunteers to transform five notorious misfits into model students — and has unintended results.
An arbitration panel is formed after a company CEO in Nigeria is sued for wrongful dismissal and rape by an employee with whom he had an affair.
An ad agency CEO is put under investigation when his ambitious protégée – and lover – accuses him of sexual harassment, vying for his top position.
When three brothers unwittingly get entangled in a murder associated with a fraudulent ashram leader, they set out to expose him to society as a fake.
After kidnapping a millionaire’s daughter, two men get swept up in a power struggle as her father enlists a brilliant cop to hunt them down.
A divorced couple decides to continue sharing a home but their already-delicate cohabiting scheme unravels when they begin dating other people.
Snowfall marks the start of Odinyule — the Viking holiday of giving! But crazy weather might cancel the tradition unless the Rescue Riders can swoop in.
After high school, a young woman marries the man of her father's choice but soon faces the possibility that her religion considers the union invalid.

Titulo: Spirit Riding Free: Ride Along Adventure
Enredo: Join Lucky and her friends on an interactive mission to save Maricela’s beloved mare from greedy horse thieves who've taken her captive with a wild herd.
A villager in Nigeria becomes the sole beneficiary of his late brother's estate in England, which, according to custom, includes his brother's fiancée.
A woman who's about to give birth finds her maternal instincts kicking in when she's abducted, imprisoned and brutalized by a vicious gang.
Fishtronaut, Marina and Zeek travel to the big city in search of Grandpa, only to find that everyone else has mysteriously vanished too.

Titulo: Alan Saldaña: Mi vida de pobre
Enredo: Mexican comic Alan Saldaña has fun with everything from the pressure of sitting in an exit row to maxing out his credit card in this stand-up special.
After his father dies, a young mechanic moves to the city to drive the old man’s taxi, and encounters assassins and a motley crew of urban weirdos.

Titulo: Pettson and Findus: The Best Christmas Ever

Enredo: After the devastating loss of a loved one, Abby forms a bond with his sister's best friend as he struggles to move on.
The Super Monsters use their powers to get their neighbors in the Halloween spirit, then help a nervous friend see there's nothing to be afraid of.
An embittered former hockey star must engage with the sport again to help his brother assemble a team for a momentous match against the British.
In this documentary, TT the Artist captures the irrepressible bounce and infectious beats of a Baltimore club scene that demands to be seen and heard.
A former addict moves to a new city with her children for a fresh start, but her struggle soon takes on an unexpected, supernatural dimension.
Shyam wakes to discover he's suspected in a murder that one journalist believes may have ties to a mysterious gangster.
When a powerful businesswoman’s political ambitions are threatened by her underworld connections, the ensuing power struggle could cost her everything.
When a mysterious woman hires Shankar to spy on a family, he must determine how his own father's abandonment figures into the situation.
Trapped in an empty building, nine people are forced to play a lethal game. All their movements will be recorded, and only one player can survive.
A former judge in retirement finds and punishes the culprits he could not convict in court, spurring a crime branch officer to investigate.

Titulo: Do Paise Ki Dhoop, Chaar Aane Ki Baarish

Enredo: After being forced to leave his country three times, a Lebanese film director traces his roots and analyzes key moments of the nation's history.
A film crew shooting in a remote forested location begins losing members one by one to a mysterious entity that they cannot see or hear.
A multigenerational household navigates daily life, evolving relationships and clashes between old and new mindsets in this light family drama.
When a city man returns to his native village for his brother’s wedding, several unforeseen snags make his visit more eventful than anticipated.
In his second stand-up special, Daniel Sosa reminisces about his childhood, ponders Mexican traditions and points out a major problem with "Coco."
When their leader is captured by an extremist organization, a special forces team stages a perilous rescue mission as time runs out.

Titulo: David Batra: Elephant in The Room

Enredo: Asked to deliver a package for a friend, Madhu gets her fiancé, Jayaganthan, to take care of it, and he then passes the task to one of his roommates.
Two cops form a task force to take down two mobsters, but when a sinister politician enters the picture, dubious loyalties and motives come to light.
Comedian Ralphie May takes to the Las Vegas stage with his raw, rollicking take on men's fashion, racism, sex and even waffles. Filmed live in 2013.
Three sisters seem to be ideal brides for three brothers. But when the girls' father won't allow the marriages, the boys use trickery to pull it off.
A group of singletons stumbles through the wild dating scene in Nairobi as two friends wonder if their relationship is more than platonic.
While in Rome to shoot his first movie, actor and industrial heir Nick becomes obsessed with a dating app that sends him into a self-destructive spiral.
When his unlucky horoscope doesn’t bode well for his future wife, an earnest bachelor goes to surprising lengths to get the family he’s always wanted.
Kaal is back – bigger and badder than ever! Can Little Singham fight the battle of a lifetime to stop the demon’s plans to wreak havoc on earth?
When his wife begins to exhibit alarming behavior, a husband tries to find whether she suffers from a personality disorder or something more sinister.
A young girl grows increasingly concerned about the rhino poaching in her village when it begins to directly impact her impoverished family.

Titulo: Merry Men: The Real Yoruba Demons
Enredo: Four of the richest bachelors in Abuja, Nigeria enjoy a life of fast cars, palatial homes and female attention while concealing their true activities.

Titulo: Jack Whitehall: Christmas with my Father

Enredo: A young lawyer who has information about counterfeit drug trafficking in Nigeria must choose between betraying his conscience or revealing the truth.
Disillusioned by life in 1970s France, a West Indian expatriate named Jimmy joins a gang of idealistic robbers, but betrayal and violence soon follow.
When the accidental death of a couple's young son sends them grieving in opposite directions, they're forced to re-examine their life and marriage.
After falling for a guest, an unsuspecting hotel staff becomes embroiled in a hostage scheme and discovers true love in an unlikely place.
After recovering from a tragic experience, a young woman makes a journey to her father's homeland and falls in love with a kind-hearted doctor.

Titulo: Quiet Victory: The Charlie Wedemeyer Story
Enredo: When high school football coach Charlie Wedemeyer is diagnosed with Lou Gehrig's disease, he perseveres in leading his team despite becoming disabled.

Titulo: Rodney Carrington: Here Comes The Truth
A Go Go Cory Carson Halloween

Enredo: A daring farmer steals illicit ivory from a group of international terrorists and must elude their dangerous and deadly games.
A fashion designer and an arrogant businessman reluctantly try to help each other after accidentally swapping phones in the airport.
An idealistic cop joins an underground police unit and battles ghoulish forces threatening the balance between the human and the supernatural realms.

Titulo: Norm of the North: King Sized Adventure
Enredo: Before planning an awesome wedding for his grandfather, a polar bear king must take back a stolen artifact from an evil archaeologist first.
French rap duo PNL deliver hypnotic visuals and perform popular tracks from their album "Dans la légende" and more at the Bercy Arena in Paris.
A freshman uninterested in joining a fraternity is convinced to pledge by a rich roommate who introduces him to a world darker than he ever dreamed.
Returning Pup Star champ Tiny has her Yorkie paws full after an evil rival replaces her with street dog Scrappy during the national competition.
This documentary dissects Lebanon's present-day paradoxes stemming from years of conflict as the director attempts to reconcile with her nation's past.
An aspiring actress is admitted to a prestigious conservatory but must pay her tuition by working as a performer for an unusual company.
With a championship on the line, Chayse and her gymnastics team look to a local break-dancer for all the right moves to rise above their competition.
This short film follows a newly displaced Syrian couple's drive around Beirut, which then morphs into a hallucinatory and nostalgic trip.
From surprise news to relationship blues, four coworkers in different stages of motherhood unite to support each other in their struggles with men.

Titulo: Carlos Ballarta: El Amor es de Putos

Enredo: This film follows the societal challenges three strangers in Beirut go through as unexpected events link their fates.
Jailed for drug trafficking while searching for the dad she's never met, a singer gets unlikely support from a crook whose love she has long rejected.
Live from Hamburg, Iranian-German comedian Enissa Amani shares her take on German engineering, tax deductions and online fan-mail etiquette.
After the election-night murder of her campaign manager at a polling site, a gubernatorial candidate challenges the corrupt incumbent's victory.

Titulo: The Remix: Hip Hop x Fashion

Enredo: Seeking to improve his combat skills, a young man falls in love with a woman with mystical powers, but his past stands in the way of their union.
This documentary follows eight women in India who struggle with self-confidence and society's expectations but rediscover themselves through running.
When their fun in the park is threatened by a neighborhood nagger, a group of friends declares war to play freely on their turf.
Go backstage with beloved rap superstar Gims in the year leading up to his major 2019 Stade de France performance in this up-close documentary.
A large immigration raid in a small town leaves emotional fallout and hard questions for its churchgoers about what it means to love thy neighbor.
When her estranged mother suddenly dies, a woman must follow the quirky instructions laid out in the will in order to collect an important inheritance.
Mexican comedian Alan Saldaña is back, poking gentle fun at himself and parceling advice, especially about how to stay married and how to be parents.
After his brother dies, wealthy Vikram reluctantly returns to India and forms a surprise bond with his orphaned nephew and the showgirl raising him.
A taxi driver new to Beirut forms an unlikely bond with a bored American Pilates instructor who loves hearing him tell stories about his past.
"Trailer Park Boys" John Paul Tremblay, Robb Wells and Mike Smith host this foulmouthed live kick-off of their Web-based Swearnet network.
Four brothers learn that they have inherited ancestral land, but must fight to claim it when a greedy feudal lord threatens to take it over.
The lives of a Mumbai man and woman who are both dealing with issues intersect through a TV dance show that she wants to win but he wants to sabotage.
The lives of a fundamentalist online troll and a woman reeling from a sex tape gone viral become dangerously intertwined in this provocative thriller.
When his employee disappears in Singapore, Shyam travels from India to investigate the absence and becomes entangled in a deadly plot.

Titulo: Martin Matte : La vie, la mort... eh la la..!
