Journey into the extraordinary world of "The Witcher" — from casting the roles to Jaskier's catchy song — in this behind-the-scenes look at the series.
In post-revolution Tehran, a wealthy Jewish businessman is summarily jailed and tortured, but along with his wife, he fights for answers and freedom.
When their respective parents oppose their union, a newly engaged couple learns that the reasons for pushback run deeper than just tribal differences.
Through the lens of faiths and cultures in seven provinces in Indonesia, this documentary follows individuals who strive to address climate change.
In the 18th century, apprentice exorcist Tom Ward is the lynchpin in a battle between good and evil when imprisoned witch Mother Malkin escapes.
A teen gamer is forced to level up to full-time babysitter when his favorite video game drops three superpowered infants from space into his backyard.

Titulo: Octonauts & the Caves of Sac Actun
Enredo: The Octonauts embark on an underwater adventure, navigating a set of challenging caves to help a small octopus friend return home to the Caribbean Sea.
Three families navigate uncertainty and struggle when cancer affects their lives and presents emotional challenges that test their bonds.
A night at a 1980s heavy metal concert hits a grisly note when new friends find themselves in the middle of a satanic murder spree.

Titulo: Berlin, Berlin: Lolle on the Run
Enredo: In this cinematic sequel to the hit TV series, Lolle has moved on from Sven and is about to marry her friend Hart – until Sven disrupts her plans.

Titulo: The Magic School Bus Rides Again Kids In Space
Enredo: The Magic School Bus kids blast into orbit — and onto the International Space Station — only to find themselves on the run from a giant tardigrade!
Comedian and "Saturday Night Live" writer Sam Jay serves up fresh takes on relationships, travel nightmares, the audacity of white people and more.
A close crew of striving New Yorkers experiences both joy and heartache in their romantic and professional lives.
When their leader is captured by an extremist organization, a special forces team stages a perilous rescue mission as time runs out.
Tumi Morake dishes out hot takes and fiery commentary about the concept of identity, politics, family life, weaves, and more in this stand-up special.
When a greedy bear steals a magic stone to keep the forest’s water for himself, a brave hedgehog and a timid squirrel must work together to retrieve it.
High in the Andes, a teenage boy and his father work together as artisans. But their bond is shattered when the son learns of his father's secret life.
This documentary reconstructs the pivotal moments that drove a man on a rampage to destroy a small town with a bulldozer he fortified in secret.
Despite leaving for college, a heartsick teen tries to build a new friendship with a kindred spirit even though she's dating her ex-boyfriend.

Titulo: The Remix: Hip Hop X Fashion
Enredo: This documentary profiles Black visionaries in fashion who rewrote narratives on the runway and turned hip-hop style into a global phenomenon.
Separated from their young son during the brutal Khmer Rouge revolution, a couple must find ways to endure while searching for their child.
At a resort getaway, the fate of two couples collides when a wife unexpectedly runs into an old flame as he hesitates to propose to his girlfriend.
From campy lies to sexy surprises, this collection of vignettes captures the follies of several men as they fumble with fidelity and relationships.
Diagnosed with colon cancer, a free-spirited man embarks on an illuminating road trip with his son through South Africa.
The forest-dwelling Lorax has to stop the short-sighted Once-ler from ruining the environment for profit in this adaptation of the Dr. Seuss classic.
An Indian intelligence agent journeys to a war-torn coastal island to break a resolute rebel group and meets a passionate journalist.
Mumbai shopkeeper Kanji Bhai files a lawsuit against God when an earthquake destroys his store and his insurance policy won't cover the damage.
A couple must endure a self-imposed quarantine and elude authorities after a mysterious virus proves lethal to the world’s female population.
Dumped by her fiancé, a sheltered young woman decides to go on her honeymoon to Europe alone, embarking on an exhilarating journey of self-discovery.
Through her diary, Anne Frank's story is retold alongside those of five Holocaust survivors in this poignant documentary from Oscar winner Helen Mirren.
A garden gnome vendor and his brother-in-law attend a trade fair in Sofia, where they accidentally stumble into shenanigans involving a mafia boss.
An ex-movie extra plans to win his wife back by making a fantasy film, but neither he nor his crew has a knack for filmmaking.
After a prank blows up a studious high school senior's life, he shares a list of certain things he wishes he'd done differently — and maybe still can.

Titulo: George Lopez: We'll Do It For Half
Enredo: Comedian George Lopez tackles the future and the past of Latinx culture in America, touching on immigration, his tough relatives, aging and much more.
This biopic maps the meteoric rise of far-right Shiv Sena party founder, Bal Thackeray, from controversial cartoonist to powerful Mumbai politician.
The daughter of a horse trainer, an ambitious girl sets her sights on becoming the first female jockey to win the Melbourne Cup. Based on a true story.
Multiple women report their husbands as missing but when it appears they are looking for the same man, a police officer traces their cryptic connection.
Multiple women report their husbands as missing but when it appears they are looking for the same man, a police officer traces their cryptic connection.
From controversial cartoonist to powerful Mumbai politician, this biopic maps the meteoric rise of far-right Shiv Sena party founder, Bal Thackeray.
A disenchanted chef tries to help her parents restore their failing hotel but cooks up feelings for an investor with his sights set on the property.
A local shop becomes a hub for young men taken with the new neighbor. But as business booms, it may leave the equally smitten storeowner heartbroken.
In 12th-century Spain, a philosopher and his profound teachings jeopardize the caliph he serves when political rivals threaten a government upheaval.
Living in Alexandria during World War II, an Egyptian teen enamored with American films dreams of making it in Hollywood.
At the peak of his career, Yehia joins a hunger strike, becomes smitten and reckons with a creative crisis — but finds a new muse.
Members of Thai girl group BNK48 share the ups and downs of preparing for the 6th Single Senbatsu General Election.
The Sultan of Egypt and Syria launches a campaign to retake Jerusalem amid the Crusades.
In 1976 Beirut, after a rendezvous with her old flame, soon-to-wed Noha witnesses a violent incident and changes course on a path to self-realization.
Following her father's death, a young woman struggles to help her mother keep the family ranch afloat while preserving a special bond with her horse.

Titulo: The Show Must Go On: The Queen + Adam Lambert Story
Enredo: With rare footage and candid interviews, this documentary details the serendipitous pairing of legendary rock band Queen and powerhouse Adam Lambert.
For a tech-savvy thief, elaborate robberies and evading the police are second nature until a private detective is hired to investigate his latest heist.
In Delhi, friends from Northeast India prepare a pungent delicacy for a wedding party, sparking conflict and comedy with their unaccustomed neighbors.
To celebrate the memory of their pal who passed away, three estranged friends attempt to reconnect on an eventful road trip from Abu Dhabi to Beirut.
The life of a seemingly ordinary high school student with a mysterious past is turned upside down when a group of strangers show up and wreak havoc.
A composer hides his love for his formerly blind ex when she returns to Egypt engaged to his childhood friend — the doctor who restored her sight.
Raised by a father to fraudulently act as one person, three identical brothers end up pining for the same woman as one triplet seeks psychiatric help.
Disillusioned with her humdrum routine, a married lawyer secretly enrolls in a dance school in this remake of the 1996 Japanese film “Shall We Dance?”
As a man fumbles to keep things in order, his assertive grandmother tries to straighten out his life when she returns to live with him.
After losing his father, a genius yet troubled aviation engineer suffering from loneliness tackles a complex project: love.
After he is rejected by the woman he loves and obesity-related issues kill his uncle, a lonely, overweight artist undergoes a major transformation.
A well-to-do British woman must venture into New Zealand's wild and dangerous unknown when her baby son is kidnapped and held for ransom.
A choreographer casts a contemporary dancer and a gifted pianist for a highly anticipated Broadway show as internal drama tries to steal the spotlight.
A guys' getaway to an isolated farm in the desert goes from fun to frightening when a mysterious guest crashes the party.
Torn between reuniting with one family and leaving another behind, Doel must choose between the two women he loves.

Titulo: Modest Heroes: Ponoc Short Films Theatre
Enredo: Two underwater siblings surviving on their own. A boy with a serious egg allergy. A man invisible to the rest of society. Three short animated tales.
In this satirical play, a wealthy Kuwaiti businessman travels to London for pleasure and encounters a host of eccentric characters.
A trio of best friends — a carefree bachelorette, a passionate mom and a perfectionist girlfriend — try to spice up their sex lives with their partners.
While running from the law, Sayed begins to work as a house servant to a wealthy family, whose divorced daughter enlists his help in a marriage scheme.

Titulo: Ben Platt Live from Radio City Music Hall
Enredo: Backed by a full band and a ready wit, actor Ben Platt opens up a very personal songbook onstage —numbers from his debut LP, "Sing to Me Instead.”
New to London, a naive and desperate teenager tries to fit in but instead becomes tragically implicated in a merciless world of gang violence.
When two unlikely friends play hooky from school, accidental encounters and otherworldly events turn their day into a whimsical coming-of-age journey.
A musician's marriage proposal to his girlfriend is denied by her mother, whose affinity for magic begins to meddle in their relationship even more.
After her husband reveals he's an undercover Mossad agent, an Egyptian woman and their children are taken to Israel, prompting an urgent rescue mission.
A woman ends up working at the same nightclub as her son’s girlfriend — who she doesn’t like — and tries to break up their relationship.
After undergoing hypnosis, Ramez finally meets the woman of his dreams — but his vision of her appearance doesn't quite match up with reality.
A wedding singer and his friends try to prove his innocence after he's accused of murder, a situation threatening his own marriage plans.
A terrifying home invasion shatters a couple's happy family life and brings their marriage to the brink as painful fallout unfolds.
After Marcos is dumped by his girlfriend, he attempts to reinvent himself as a modern man with the help of a childhood friend and an online guru.
Armed with a thirst for revenge, a vigilante makes justice her business after being hired by various women to seduce and humiliate their rapists.
Dylan Mohan Gray examines Africa's AIDS crisis and activists' battle with pharmaceutical companies to make life-saving HIV drugs more affordable.
Drugs and addiction endanger the love — and lives — of two childhood sweethearts struggling to survive the perils of a precarious world.
Join former first lady Michelle Obama in an intimate documentary looking at her life, hopes and connection with others as she tours with "Becoming."
Jerry Seinfeld takes the stage in New York and tackles talking vs. texting, bad buffets vs. so-called "great" restaurants and the magic of Pop Tarts.

Titulo: Luccas Neto em: Acampamento de Férias 2
Enredo: Luccas and his band of buddies make music and mischief at a new summer camp, where they face off with talented rivals and their tough coach.
When a rebellious teen searches for her unknown roots, it leads her to the sport of dirt track racing and a discovery she didn't expect.

Titulo: Cracked Up: The Darrell Hammond Story
Enredo: "Saturday Night Live" star Darrell Hammond reveals the extreme abuse he suffered during childhood, a trauma that nearly destroyed his life as an adult.
When smart but cash-strapped teen Ellie Chu agrees to write a love letter for a jock, she doesn't expect to become his friend — or fall for his crush.

Titulo: Thomas & Friends: Thomas and the Royal Engine
Enredo: An invitation from the Queen sends Thomas and the crew to London as they weave through delays and debacles while racing to a royal celebration.
In an eastern Turkish town, suitors knock on the door of the mayor and father of three beautiful daughters who choose to follow their own paths.
Things look up for a Chennai man struggling to make ends meet when he falls for a politician’s daughter – until he gets entangled in a murder case.
When a local musician and his band are forced to perform in honor of a right-wing coup, his daughter schemes to make their music subversive instead.
A former goalkeeper-turned-talent scout embarks on a mischievous adventure to recruit players for Egyptian football clubs.
A matriarch and her grandson forge a special bond during family picnics every two months, until her health causes a conflict among the relatives.
When his jealous sister plots to wreck his engagement, a young man does everything he can to protect his betrothed from her devious schemes.
Upon his return to Istanbul, an expat writer-editor finds himself stranded inside a web of tangled relationships after his filmmaker friend vanishes.
As an honest locksmith scrambles to pay his late father's hefty debt to the mafia, he crosses paths with a woman in similar trouble and falls for her.
Burdened by troubles and caught between cultures, Riza takes a job as a mall Santa and finds that real life may not be so different from make-believe.
A gang leader recruits a suicidal Superman impersonator, while a woman driving a hot car linked to the gang plots revenge against them and their hero.

Titulo: We'll Be Right Back After The Break
Enredo: While fighting a child custody battle against his father-in-law, a taxi driver loses his memory when his son is kidnapped.
To keep the band together, Selly tries to earn money by making an appearance at the birthday party of a mobster's daughter — until he gets kidnapped.
When a lazy young man replaces his father as the elevator operator of a posh residential complex, what he sees as menial work soon takes on new meaning.
Separated by distance and circumstance, two bitter rivals cross paths when the perils of the drug trade unexpectedly unite them.
A footballer for a local club aspires to join the big leagues then gets his shot at going pro, fueling his team's rise to victory.
When his powerful crime czar boss kills the man he considered a mentor, a young gangster on the rise goes to war in order to get revenge.
On his wedding day, an arrogant, greedy accountant experiences a series of calamities that keep replaying as he lives the same day over and over again.
For decades, a nice Jewish couple ran Circus of Books, a porn shop and epicenter for gay LA. Their director daughter documents their life and times.
Comedian Maurício Meirelles explores his chaotic mind with scathingly funny views on family, prejudices, turtles and more in this stand-up special.
Mistaking the sleeping passenger on his train for a drunk, a young man posts a picture of him online, unaware of his impulsive act's ugly repercussions.

Titulo: Tiffany Haddish: She Ready! From the Hood To Hollywood!
Enredo: Comedic breakout Tiffany Haddish delivers a riotous stand-up ripe with the unpretentious and filthy tales of her meteoric rise to stardom.
A documentary on why and how "Money Heist" sparked a wave of enthusiasm around the world for a lovable group of thieves and their professor.

Titulo: Chhota Bheem and the Curse of Damyaan
Enredo: An evil demon who traded his freedom for immortality lures Chhota Bheem and his friends to the city of Sonapur with tales of hidden treasure.
Swedish comedian David Batra gets personal as he playfully details the perks and pitfalls of being married to a recently resigned political leader.
Best friends since childhood, a righteous cop and a lawyer who represents criminals in court become rivals when they fall for the same woman.
An industrialist's daughter is forced to marry a rich heir by her greedy grandmother as her adopted sister bonds with the charismatic wedding planner.
God-fearing Pandit Krishna Kant loses everything and turns to a life of crime after his landlord tries to rape his wife and tears his family apart.
Meeting after many years, a makeup artist and her grandmother revisit tensions from an old family feud that still hang heavy between them.
An American kid obsessed with the undead befriends and offers to help a young vampire whose family is being targeted by a merciless vampire hunter.
Facing a drought, a hungry tiger and a noble cow have an extraordinary encounter in this fable based on a children’s book and a Kannada folk song.

Titulo: Dave Chappelle: The Kennedy Center Mark Twain Prize for American Humor
Enredo: Dave Chappelle is awarded the prestigious Mark Twain Prize for American Humor in a star-studded ceremony from the Kennedy Center in Washington, D.C.
Stripped of his heritage at a residential school, an indigenous student finds refuge on the rink when he discovers a passion for hockey.

Titulo: Through My Father's Eyes: The Ronda Rousey Story
Enredo: This documentary chronicles former Olympian and UFC champion Ronda Rousey's ascent to iconic status in the world of mixed martial arts.

Titulo: Willy and the Guardians of the Lake: Tales from the Lakeside Winter Adventure
Enredo: As winter approaches the lake, a common threat rattles the Verdies and Grimps as Willy Whistle looks to seize his chance to become a guardian.
A look at the making of one of the first series to authentically portray and explore issues in a Hasidic community as they pertain to women's lives.
As a teen languishes during a spiritless road trip, she learns of the troubles in her parents' marriage as a crisis in her country looms.
A young girl passionate about AI sets out to make an impact as three friends become crime-fighting superheroes. Based on the hit animated web series.
Over a series of birthdays, a happy-go-lucky, commitment-averse fashion designer strives to bring a bit of calm to her chaotic love life.
Set against the 2015 Rugby World Cup, this documentary captures the allure of rugby as told by fans, players and others who have touched the game.

Titulo: Digs & Discoveries: All Track's Lead to Rome
Enredo: After being introduced to Italy's ancient history, Thomas sets out to prove his expertise until his curiosity lands him in trouble in an old mine.
Amidst Italy's ancient sites and hidden treasures, Thomas is inspired to make his own special discovery, sending him on a journey to find a lost legend.
Thomas and the steam trains spring into action when Porter and the diesel engines run into a series of accidents that throw their deliveries off track.
A fearless teen leans into the rush of high-speed go-kart racing, backed by good friends — and a surly ex-driver who becomes his coach.
In this silent short set in 1970s Pakistan, 14-year-old Pari longs to be a pilot, unaware that her father plans to marry her off to a much older man.
An inseparable couple struggles to stay together when betrayal threatens to tear their lives apart.
A turbulent past haunts Jonas, who recalls his teenage love affair with the impulsive, twisted and yet irresistible Nathan.

Titulo: Twin Murders: the Silence of the White City
Enredo: A detective returns to Vitoria-Gasteiz to solve murders mimicking those allegedly committed by a serial killer who's about to be released from prison.
42-year-old Viorel, a distraught engineer, takes drastic measures to end his emotional suffering after enduring a devastating divorce.
This intimate portrait depicts the rise of artist Lil Peep, whose genre-bending music attracted a massive following and ultimately defined his life.
Hidden away by her eccentric father, a mysterious young girl uncovers frightening truths when she starts to make contact with the outside world.
Finally comfortable in his skin, seasoned comic David A. Arnold shares his talent for doing nothing, how he's petty and why divorce saves marriages.
Determined to bring traditional bhangra to the world stage, a dancer preps for an international competition against a rival with dreams of her own.

Titulo: Calico Critters: Everyone's Big Dream Flying in the Sky
Enredo: In the Hazelnut Chipmunk Family, Dominic is a little boy who loves to play, but a big moment will make him more grown-up on one memorable day.

Titulo: ZZ TOP: THAT LITTLE OL' BAND FROM TEXAS
Enredo: This documentary delves into the mystique behind the blues-rock trio and explores how the enigmatic band created their iconic look and sound.
Two teens facing personal struggles form a powerful bond as they embark on a cathartic journey chronicling the wonders of Indiana.
Three couples, each in different phases of romance, head to Ibadan for a fun and frisky holiday. But secrets soon spill, causing trouble in paradise.

Titulo: Pete Davidson: Alive From New York
Enredo: Comedian and "SNL" star Pete Davidson drops a candid and intimate stand-up special shot live in New York City.
Traumatized, violent and yearning for love, 9-year-old Benni bonds with a gruff mentor as child-services workers struggle to find her a home.
Fresh off a bad relationship, thrill-seeking Martha finds romance and danger with Francis, a hit man who's decided to turn the tables on his clients.
A young woman conducts a search for her twin sister, who disappeared in a notorious area of Japan known as the Suicide Forest.
Clawdeen wants to turn an abandoned power station into a salon for monsters and "normies" alike. But Moanica's got a shocking plan to ruin everything.
An adventure-loving young woman catches the attention of a handsome beau in this musical celebration of love, friends and fate.
In 18th-century India, a Maratha commander leads his army in preparation for a fierce battle against Afghan invaders in this film based on real events.
Luca follows in his father's footsteps to rescue his mother from evil Ladja. Finding the heavenly hero who wields the Zenithian sword is his only hope.
In this interactive special, Harold and George need your decision-making skills to stop Krupp from blowing their beloved treehouse to smithereens.
Director Alfonso Cuarón reflects on the childhood memories, period details and creative choices that shaped his Academy Award-winning film "ROMA."
When a new, deadly narcotic sweeps the American Southwest, a Border Patrol agent must contend with a task force that challenges his duties and morals.
As corrupt governments fail to stop the slaughter of elephants for ivory, an 80-year-old woman and a crew of rangers bravely try to end the poaching.
Alluding to "For Whom the Bell Tolls," this drama follows a fugitive guerrilla, deaf after an explosion, as he tries to survive in 1944 northern Spain.
Although Nisha falls for Prem, she agrees to marry his older brother for the good of their families. But fate may have other plans for the lovebirds.
A U.S. Marshal arrives at a small town in Nevada, only to learn that his preacher brother is dead after standing up to the town's mayor and outlaws.

Titulo: Night on Earth: Shot in the Dark
Enredo: This look behind the scenes shows how worldwide camera crews climbed, dived and froze to capture the documentary's groundbreaking night footage.
A scheming matriarch plots to cut off her disabled stepson and his wife from the family fortune, creating a division within the clan.
Trapped by society and familial obligations, a young manga artist goes on an unconventional journey for sexual freedom and personal liberation.
From first crushes to post-marriage relationships, love and connection are at the heart of the four interwoven stories in this anthology film.
An inexperienced murder detective joins a desperate search for a deranged serial killer who possesses a deep obsession with young women’s skin.
As his children plot his death to claim their inheritance, an aging patriarch leaves home, befriending a spunky boy who adds direction to his life.
A detective interrogates a monkey who is suspected of murder.
During the internet's infancy, a vulnerable woman follows her sister into the sex industry as a webcam model but her sudden popularity tests their bond.
Exploring their sexual identities in the face of the patriarchal rules of their Assamese village, a teenager and her two friends are rocked by tragedy.
A cartel boss is released from prison and unknowingly put in the care of a vengeful nurse, whose life was tragically impacted by the drug lord.
Brilliant young students discover a breakthrough that could change humankind, but soon find themselves the subjects of a much bigger experiment.
After a trip to China, a struggling entrepreneur returns to India as the supplier of an illegal aphrodisiac — but all he ends up stimulating is chaos.
When Emilio (Oscar Martínez) is diagnosed with Alzheimer's disease, he and his family embark on a quest to reunite him with his childhood crush.

Titulo: All the Freckles in the World
Enredo: Thirteen-year-old José Miguel is immune to 1994 World Cup fever until he realizes soccer is the only way to win the heart of his crush.
Bank chairman Charles Bunbury – who knows next to nothing about banking – fights to save both his company and his marriage from disaster.
The directors of Emmy-nominated "Lust Stories" (Zoya Akhtar, Anurag Kashyap, Dibakar Banerjee and Karan Johar) reunite for this quartet of thrillers.

Titulo: Pokémon the Movie: Power of Us
Enredo: Ash and Pikachu journey to Fula City for its Wind Festival. When disaster looms, they must work together with a group of misfits to save the day!
Caught between family pressures and small-time crime-fighting, a pair of bumbling cops tries to bust a massive drug deal and go down in history.
In this intimate documentary, former Uruguayan President José "Pepe" Mujica talks about lessons he learned while in prison, his ideals and the future.
Mysterious goons chase teenage slacker Angelino through chaotic Dark Meat City as he uncovers secret powers that could be the key to saving the world.
To earn his place in heaven, legendary Mexican actor-singer Pedro Infante is sent back to Earth in an impersonator's body to mend his womanizing ways.
Dreaming of a better life, an imperiled prostitute crosses paths with a wealthy company heir who’s been transformed into a child by his evil uncle.
Eleven emerging Bangladeshi filmmakers present a collection of gritty shorts centered on the capital city and the people living in its margins.
A newly engaged couple's romantic vacation in Jamaica turns into a mischievous adventure that tests their union in wild and unexpected ways.
When a couple leaning toward divorce meets with a pastor for counseling, an unexpected development shakes up their marriage.
An unapologetic lothario sets out to seduce three ex-flames – but gets an unexpected education in love along the way.
Engrossed in her career, a young woman reluctantly yields to her father's plan to set her up on 10 dates to find a suitable husband.
After his father passes, the heir to a retail empire returns to take over the family business but faces a controversy involving laundering and murder.

Titulo: Jack Whitehall: Christmas with My Father
Enredo: Jack Whitehall invites his notoriously stuffy father onstage in London's West End for a Christmas comedy extravaganza, complete with celebrity guests.
As controversy surrounds the evangelical church he helped found, Edir Macedo must juggle betrayals, politics and personal loss in this biopic sequel.
A successful actress with an abusive husband confides in friends who have troubling relationship issues of their own.
After a woman is severely beaten at home, her strong-willed friends take a stand against their husbands to seek justice for domestic abuse victims.
When two sisters travel from Canada to Punjab to visit their maternal family, they discover an opportunity to mend a broken bond with their grandmother.
From romantic pursuits to their friendship, a trio of young men navigate the complexities of relationships while sharing a London apartment.
This documentary examines the influence of Hong Kong's martial arts cinema on filmmaking from the Shaw Brothers to modern-day Hollywood blockbusters.

Titulo: Guatemala: Heart of the Mayan World
Enredo: From Sierra de las Minas to Esquipulas, explore Guatemala's cultural and geological wealth, including ancient Mayan cities and other natural wonders.
Nollywood star Ramsey Nouah learns that someone is impersonating him and breaks out of a mental institution to expose the imposter.

Titulo: Kalushi: The Story of Solomon Mahlangu
Enredo: The life and times of iconic South African liberation fighter Solomon Mahlangu, who battled the forces of apartheid, come into focus.
The girls of Ōarai High must face off against a formidable university team in a fierce tank battle to once again avoid closure of their school.

Titulo: Mike Birbiglia: What I Should Have Said Was Nothing: Tales from My Secret Public Journal
Enredo: Mike Birbiglia performs in this live concert special that features a riotous selection of the unique insights and observations culled from his diary.
Lorena Ramírez of Mexico's Rarámuri community lives a pastoral life – except when she straps on her sandals to compete as an ultramarathon runner.
Determined to save an Amazon tribe being squeezed by logging, a group of students finds nothing but trouble when their plane crashes in the jungle.
In the most remote areas of the Amazon jungle, a writer and his anthropologist friend meet communities who have resisted change for centuries.
Mía's vacation with her dad is disrupted by the surprise arrival of Lupe, Mercedes, Juanma and Álvaro as their school drama moves lakeside.
The seniors in Sakuragaoka High School's music club live out the graduation trip of their dreams when they celebrate by performing in London.
A trio of filmmakers treks across India to explore the correlation between vanishing rivers, massive energy projects and renewable energy sources.

Titulo: Fadily Camara : La plus drôle de tes copines
Enredo: Irrepressible French comedian Fadily Camara weaves jokes, vivid characters and physical comedy into a lively stand-up show at La Cigale in Paris.

Titulo: Jeff Garlin: Our Man In Chicago
Enredo: Comedian Jeff Garlin (unintentionally) celebrates his 37th year of stand-up and shares his learnings on love, loss, success and food addiction.
As three kingdoms struggle for control of a walled city, a figure with a rare power spins a web of intrigue that entangles a king's court.

Titulo: Minimalism: A Documentary About the Important Things
Enredo: People dedicated to rejecting the American ideal that things bring happiness are interviewed in this documentary showing the virtues of less is more.

Titulo: 100 Things to do Before High School
Enredo: Led by seventh-grader C.J., three students who have been warned about the dangers of high school decide to make the best of their middle-school years.
An eccentric game designer builds a library full of traps and tricks for a group of kids who score the chance to navigate his elaborate scavenger hunt.
A trio of siblings gets trapped in a secret temple, where they must navigate a risky obstacle course to make it out. Inspired by the ‘90s game show.
Two girls realize they're both visiting grandparents they’ve never met and decide to switch places to see how the other half lives.
With Christmas just around the corner, sisters Miranda and Lyla bring their families to their childhood home, where rivalries don't take a holiday.

Titulo: The House of Flowers Presents: The Funeral
Enredo: The de la Mora siblings publicly mourn the death of their mother amid multiple surprises and mishaps at Virginia's funeral.

Titulo: The Old Thieves: The Legend of Artegios
Enredo: While carrying out prison sentences, five notorious thieves in Mexico City share their principles, preferred methods and respect for the craft.
This introspective rockumentary follows the career triumphs and intimate moments of legendary Mexican band Zoé as they embark on a global tour.
Argentine comedian Grego Rossello takes the stage in Buenos Aires to share his takes on modern stardom, airline dining, brotherly love and more.
In his first stand-up special, Arsenio Hall discusses getting older, the changing times and culture, social issues and even bothersome baby toes.
This documentary captures the joy and heartbreak of families separated by the U.S.-Mexico border sharing a short but bittersweet reunion in 2018.

Titulo: My Next Guest with David Letterman and Shah Rukh Khan
Enredo: "King of Bollywood" Shah Rukh Khan opens up about his rise to fame, his family and his billions of fans as he and Dave meet up in Mumbai and New York.

Titulo: Master Z: The Ip Man Legacy
Enredo: In this spin-off, a martial arts expert once defeated by Ip Man is forced to abandon his reclusive lifestyle to combat a rising Chinese triad.
A sketchy arms transaction in a deserted warehouse turns into a free-for-all when the two sides engage in a take-no-prisoners shootout.
For the crew trapped aboard a sunken Russian submarine the deadliest threat is the bureaucracy on land. Based on a true story.
After his girlfriend wins the Miss Nigeria pageant, a young man faces unexpected competition of his own when he joins her on a campaign in South Africa.
A teacher turns to a dubious man to raise money for her daughter's life-saving surgery, a crisis that is unexpectedly catapulted to a national stage.
Special Forces trainer James Wilks asks elite athletes to compare the merits of meat, protein and plants for building strength. Spoiler: plants win.

Titulo: Martin Matte: La vie, la mort...eh la la..!
Enredo: Quebecois comedy star Martin Matte serves up embarrassing personal stories, a solution for social media trolls and more in this unpredictable special.
Singer-songwriter Gen Hoshino takes the stage at the sold out Tokyo Dome in his highly anticipated 2019 Pop Virus dome tour.

Titulo: Home Is Where the Killer Is
Enredo: Recovering from cancer, a young woman thinks she’s found a friend when she rents a room from a caring ex-doctor. But empathy soon becomes obsession.
A robbery leaves a proprietor penniless before his wedding, but becoming a son-in-law to a second family might be the financial solution he needs.
Shunned by his country due to religion, Abdus Salam strives for an achievement that would define modern physics and redefine his place back home.
This compilation for preschoolers features a peppy young bus and his first life experiences where bumps in the road won't stop him from a fun ride.
Nikki Glaser bares all in a blistering stand-up special about sex, sobriety and getting over her own insecurities. And she won't spare you the details.
A clumsy but cheerful fisheries student struggles to find her place at a research institute renowned for its tuna cultivation. The work isn't easy.
A surly septuagenarian gets another chance at her 20s after having her photo snapped at a studio that magically takes 50 years off her life.
A surly septuagenarian gets another chance at her 20s after having her photo snapped at a studio that magically takes 50 years off her life.
An American man in the midst of a mid-life crisis travels to the French countryside to find a new lease on life.

Titulo: Do Paise Ki Dhoop Chaar Aane Ki Baarish
Enredo: When a sex worker hires a gay songwriter to care for her disabled son, the ensuing bonds that form offer a complex portrayal of love and family.
When struggling singer Onur decides to return to his old job, incurable klutz Şeref organizes a surprise tour full of pitfalls and mishaps.
This moving documentary chronicles the unshakeable romance between a couple who met and fell in love while imprisoned in a Nazi concentration camp.

Titulo: The Crystal Calls Making the Dark Crystal: Age of Resistance
Enredo: Go behind the scenes with stars, puppeteers and creators as they bring Jim Henson's magical world of Thra back to life in a sweeping fantasy series.
When his chatty nature lands him in trouble, an unlucky meatball seller flees Istanbul and finds a new life on a beautiful island.
From a schoolboy’s crush to a middle-aged bachelor’s office romance, four love stories spanning age, religion and status unfold in a small Indian town.
Bogged down with money problems, a couple grows cautious of each other but hit the lottery and decide to stay together – till death do they part.

Titulo: American Factory: A Conversation with the Obamas
Enredo: Barack and Michelle Obama talk with directors Steven Bognar and Julia Reichert about the documentary and the importance of storytelling.
Rushing to pay off a loan shark, a young man breaks into a bungalow to steal the cash, unprepared for the dog standing guard – or the trouble inside.
In this documentary, the director remembers a sister who left behind her life under Brazil’s dictatorship and moved to New York with dreams of acting.
A pregnancy forces an actress out of her latest play and into a difficult confrontation with her own rapidly transforming reflection.
When an unattractive man gets engaged to a beautiful woman, their families oppose the union and the priest set to perform the ceremony is kidnapped.
As a series of murders hit close to home, a video game designer with post-traumatic stress must confront her demons, or risk becoming their victim.
As a series of murders hit close to home, a video game designer with post-traumatic stress must confront her demons, or risk becoming their victim.
As a series of murders hit close to home, a video game designer with PTSD must confront her demons, or risk becoming their victim.
Years spent recording footage of creatures from every corner of the globe is bound to produce a bit of drama. Here's a behind-the-scenes look.
When Zim reappears to begin the next phase of his evil alien plan to conquer Earth, his nemesis Dib Membrane sets out to unmask him once and for all.
A dying tycoon has his consciousness transplanted into the body of a healthy young man, only to make a troubling discovery about the body's origin.
Bodybuilder and two-time Mr. Universe, Calum von Moger, reflects on his rise to fame and battle to come back from a debilitating injury.
This documentary follows the controversy surrounding the 2010 murders of two students, who were framed as criminals and killed by the Mexican military.

Titulo: Colin Quinn: Red State Blue State
Enredo: Stand-up comedian Colin Quinn calls out the hypocrisies of the left and the right in this special based on his politically charged Off-Broadway show.
In a witty solo show, Brent Morin serves up infectious laughs on the agony of puberty, hot guy problems and the time a girl dumped him for a magician.
Nothing is sacred in this show from Australian comic Jim Jefferies, whether it’s the mother of his child, auditioning disabled actors, or gun control.
A steroid peddler explains how he went from an unlicensed anti-aging expert to the point man for the biggest scandal in baseball history.

Titulo: Sebastian Maniscalco: Why Would You Do That
Enredo: Sebastian Maniscalco delivers an expressive stand-up at the legendary Beacon Theatre on Whole Foods, family nicknames and dodging obnoxious neighbors.
A mother and young son escape into their own imaginations to ignore the reality of their lives in rural Mexico.
A young chauffeur who's at a crossroads in his life escorts a pair of clients around Barcelona and becomes embroiled in their mysterious quest.
When a student's suicide rattles an all-girls Catholic school, a clairvoyant guidance counselor leans on a ghost to uncover the convent's abusive past.
Stranded in the woods and eyeballed by twisted hunters, members of a women’s volleyball team bump it up in the most dangerous game of their lives.
In this psychological thriller, painter Lorenzo's life spirals out of control as he fears his wife is trying to isolate him from their infant son.
Feeling guilty after a high-speed chase leaves a girl dead, a determined sergeant pursues the crime boss who triggered the fatal car accident.
When actor David Harbour finds lost footage of his father's disastrous televised stage play of a literary classic, he uncovers shocking family secrets.
Hoping to reunite with a dying friend, two longtime pals re-create their desert road trip from Spain to Mali, bringing along his estranged daughter.
Farmers, scientists and industry insiders delve into the hidden costs and consequences of global dairy production and offer up possible solutions.
The spotlight's on Parchís, a record company-created Spanish boy/girl band that had unprecedented success with Top 10 songs and hit films in the '80s.
In a comedy special directed by Spike Jonze, Aziz Ansari shares deep personal insights and hilarious takes on wokeness, family and the social climate.
Experience the highlights of Argentine soccer team Club Atlético River Plate's long history, from its early development to its major victories.
Filmed over three years in 10 countries, this documentary gives voice to the women who have become victims of sexual violence as weapons of war.
Colombian photojournalist Jesús Abad Colorado shares the stories behind a series of civil war photographs he captured throughout the '80s and '90s.
When a gun-toting rebel tries to rescue her kidnapped sister, she finds herself up against a widely feared desperado and a cursed guardian of treasure.
In a short musical film directed by Paul Thomas Anderson, Thom Yorke of Radiohead stars in a mind-bending visual piece. Best played loud.

Titulo: Hikaru Utada Laughter in the Dark Tour 2018
Enredo: Celebrating twenty years since her debut, Hikaru Utada takes the stage at Makuhari Messe for the final performance of her Laughter in the Dark Tour.
After the brutal murders of their loved ones, three individuals share how they healed through forgiveness in this documentary presented by Aamir Khan.
Family patriarch Elías begins to unravel after the death of his wife – which casts a suspicious light on her tragic accident.
Fifteen years after the Second Impact, apathetic teen Shinji joins his father's group NERV to fight the Angels. But the truth may destroy them all.
Seele orders an all-out attack on NERV, aiming to destroy the Evas before Gendo can trigger Third Impact and Instrumentality under his control.
Fiercely independent and disillusioned with love, a teen DJ is determined to chart her own path, till a pop heartthrob falls for her awesome mix.

Titulo: Oprah Presents When They See Us Now
Enredo: Oprah Winfrey talks with the exonerated men once known as the Central Park Five, plus the cast and producers who tell their story in "When They See Us."
Comedian Jo Koy takes center stage in Hawaii and shares his candid take on cultural curiosities, filter-free fatherhood and more.
An artist muddles through a midlife crisis while trying to balance his dimming career with a yearning to be a better father.
When a sacred statue is taken from his Andean village, a spirited boy who dreams of becoming a shaman goes on a brave mission to get it back.
After an adventurous teen with a heart defect bonds with an unruly stallion, she trains to compete as an amateur jockey in a life-threatening race.
A woman sexually assaulted by her new boss's brother-in-law tries to move on as if nothing happened, but the night weighs heavily on her mind and body.
A former class bully reaches out to the deaf girl he'd tormented in grade school. He feels unworthy of redemption but tries to make things right.
Despondent on a desolate island, a suicidal sheep is thrown a lifeline by a quirky salesman, who offers him the gift of a lifetime.
Viral video star Miranda Sings and her real-world alter ego Colleen Ballinger share the stage in a special packed with music, comedy and "magichinry."
Close to paying off her debts, a Nigerian sex worker in Austria coaches a reluctant novice, and assesses the risks of taking a faster path to freedom.
In this twisty horror-thriller, a once-promising music prodigy reconnects with her former mentors, only to find them taken with a talented new pupil.

Titulo: The Man Who Feels No Pain
Enredo: Leveraging his ability to withstand pain, a young man trains to follow in the footsteps of his martial-arts hero in this high-action, meta comedy.
This intimate documentary follows a group of Syrian children refugees who narrowly escape a life of torment and integrate into a foreign land.
Seeking answers after a life-changing incident in 2012, filmmaker Hernán Zin interviews other war reporters about the personal toll of their work.
When a schoolteacher inherits an adorable pug, she has to find a way to take care of it while dealing with her flatlining love life.
Wanting his missing father to come home, a Kashmiri boy repeatedly attempts to call God for help – until one day, a hardened army officer picks up.
This celebration of the groundbreaking comedy show "Laugh-In" stars Lily Tomlin, Snoop Dogg, Billy Crystal, Tiffany Haddish, Neil Patrick Harris and more.

Titulo: Merata: How Mum Decolonised the Screen
Enredo: New Zealand film archivist Heperi Mita traces the cinematic legacy of his mother and trailblazing Maori filmmaker Merata Mita.
Fresh out of juvenile detention in Marseille, 17-year-old Zach falls for a young prostitute and soon faces a dire dilemma while working as a pimp.
After her partner cheats on her, an architect returns to her hometown to reassess her life with the help of her eccentric family. Based on the novel.
After starting a family of his very own in America, a gay filmmaker documents his loving, traditional Chinese family's process of acceptance.
On the run from a dogged internal affairs agent, a corrupt cop reluctantly teams up with a defiant teen to unravel a conspiracy – before it's too late.
Go behind the scenes as four determined women – including Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez – challenge big-money politicians in the 2018 race for Congress.
When a neighbor blocks their view of the city with a commercial billboard, a Hong Kong family resorts to drastic, imaginative measures to take it down.
When his daughter and son-in-law fall prey to a scam, Istanbul con man Asım Noyan meets his match in a madcap kingpin of an underground gambling world.
It lit up jazz and hip-hop – and ignited a war on drugs steeped in racial injustice. Experts explore America's complicated relationship with weed.
A dejected small-town music teacher grapples with guilt and regret when his ex-pupil who once loved him returns home as the star he always wanted to be.
A willful young woman is hired to design a garden at Versailles for Louis XIV. Soon, she's ensnared in political and romantic complications.
Comedian Franco Escamilla shares stories about parenting his children when they get into trouble, with reflections on gender, friendship and romance.
This intimate, in-depth look at Beyoncé's celebrated 2018 Coachella performance reveals the emotional road from creative concept to cultural movement.
When a prank goes wrong, a shy kid from Compton is sent away for murder. Four years later, he’s back and out for revenge on homecoming weekend.
Ahead of her wedding, Kübra is possessed by demons. When an examination reveals more horror, her friend, a psychiatrist, tries to perform an exorcism.
A pregnant Liss Pereira shares hilariously uncomfortable truths about sex, love, attraction and the lies we tell in modern relationships.
An aspiring musician battles age-old caste divides to be able to learn the art of a classical instrument from a traditionalist, veteran percussionist.
An affable, newly appointed college warden proves to be no ordinary man when an old enemy resurfaces and exposes his complicated, violent past.
After failing out of art school and taking a humdrum office job, a whimsical painter gets a chance to fulfill her lifelong dream of adopting a unicorn.
A college stud tries to level up his relationship with a computer science major after becoming attracted to her skills in an online role-playing game.
A man returns home to Atlanta to try and turn around his family's struggling restaurant with the help of a new chicken recipe.
On India's Independence Day, a zany mishap in a Mumbai chawl disrupts a young love story while compelling the residents to unite in aid of a little boy.
Alone in Finland, a retired Mexican boxer lives in desolation under the weight of an agonizing past, until he gets a shot at redemption in the ring.
An urban legend about a duffel bag of cocaine buried in the Caribbean leads a misfit band to hatch a nutball plan to find it in this comic documentary.
Adapted from a best-selling novel, this horror film shows Risa befriending ghosts until an evil spirit tries to take her sister to the other side.
In this adaptation of the comic strip, Juan López must balance an office job with heroic feats to save the love of his life and native planet Chitón.
Love can be complicated, especially when Vince agrees to secretly woo Kath via text on behalf of James – while falling for her, too.
Amy Schumer spills on her new marriage, personal growth, making a baby and her mom's misguided advice in a special that's both raunchy and sincere.
A PR agent trying to find her stolen phone, a politician in trouble, and a fading celebrity find their lives intertwining in unexpected, messy ways.
When his son's mom runs afoul of Paris's criminal underworld, a thrill-seeking superbike racer begins moonlighting as a drug courier to clear her debt.
Naval unit PASKAL is among the most elite special forces in Malaysia. But all bets are off when one of its own stages a hijacking. Based on true events.
When her romance with a lustful marquis takes an unwelcome turn, a wealthy widow concocts a scheme to get revenge – with help from a younger woman.
A devastating breakup with her boyfriend may be the start of a new beginning for Mace, thanks to an adventurous and kind stranger named Anthony.
An aspiring musician battles age-old caste divides to be able to learn the art of a classical instrument from a traditionalist, veteran percussionist.
An ex-colonel forms a special paramilitary group focused on combatting drug trafficking on the Paraguayan border.
Rocco needs to hire a bride so he can access his trust fund. Rocky desperately needs a job. Their marriage starts out fake, but ends up as much more.

Titulo: Zach Galifianakis: Live at the Purple Onion
Enredo: The unorthodox, piano-playing stand-up star Zach Galifianakis makes a splash on the scene and serves up a healthy dose of his signature wit.
A Catalán prisoner at a Nazi concentration camp uses his office job to steal photo negatives of the atrocities committed there. Based on true events.
Powerlifter Matt Kroczaleski faced his greatest challenge when he came out as transgender. This documentary captures his transition into a woman.
Extreme pressure from his father to excel at school during childhood has dangerous psychological effects on a brilliant but suicidal man’s adult life.
A hard-driving submarine captain is hired to steal gold from a sunken Nazi sub, but there's no honor among thieves during this underwater heist.
Disparate characters, including an aspiring time traveler, a phony chef, a drug-addicted waitress and several others, share a surprising connection.
Inspired by the movie "Thelma & Louise," three young people with Down syndrome leave the institution where they live to take a road trip together.
On the incandescent shores of Goa, a young man tumbles down a mind-bending – and soon dangerous – series of trips after taking hallucinatory drugs.
While taking shelter from a Mumbai monsoon, an investment banker forms an unlikely connection with a naïve prostitute over the course of the night.
Killed too soon due to a clerical error in heaven, a man is sent back to earth with a new lease on life, this time in the body of his portly friend.
A renowned music teacher mentors a promising young singer, but when her fame begins to overshadow his own, he lets jealousy and competition take over.
When caste discrimination prevents a villager from giving his deceased father a rightful burial, he takes his fight for equality to court.
When Superman and the other Justice League superheroes start disappearing, it's up to Batman to unravel the caper and save the day.

Titulo: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes: Black Panther
Enredo: When Thanos joins forces with villains Killmonger and Klaue to destroy Earth, Black Panther rushes to stop them from stealing Wakanda's vibranium.

Titulo: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes: Guardians of the Galaxy
Enredo: The Guardians are on a mission to deliver the Build Stone to the Avengers before the Ravagers, Thanos and his underlings steal it from them.

Titulo: Maharaja: The Story of Ranjit Singh
Enredo: The tale of legendary warrior king Ranjit Singh, and his rise to establishing Punjab’s Sikh empire, comes to life in this animated feature.

Titulo: Gabriel "Fluffy" Iglesias: One Show Fits All
Enredo: Gabriel "Fluffy" Iglesias discusses his teenage son and encounters with Snoop Dogg, Chris Rock and Vicente Fernández in this stand-up special for 2019.
A deputy curator of a chaebol-funded art gallery and her husband, a politically ambitious economics professor, will do anything to join the über-elite.
A grieving filmmaker struggling to keep custody of his young son after his wife's death uses magical, imaginary stories to maintain their bond.
After saving an unwed expectant mother who's injured in a car accident, a happily married man takes her as his second wife – without telling his first.
In this sequel to the award-winning 2015 film, Pras, Arini and Meirose face new challenges that could change the dynamic of their unique love triangle.
A teen's eerie visions become increasingly frequent and terrifying after her longtime friend gets a girlfriend and his abusive dad is strangely killed.
A sly art dealer tries to revive the career of his longtime pal, a surly painter, with a risky plan that tests their morals and friendship.
Inspired by his love affair with a conservative lawyer, the lead singer of a struggling garage band pens a hit song that propels him to fame.

Titulo: FYRE: The Greatest Party That Never Happened
Enredo: The Fyre Festival was billed as a luxury music experience on a posh private island, but it failed spectacularly in the hands of a cocky entrepreneur.
This documentary captures the environmental and societal impact of Brazil's Cerrado savanna suffering from severe deforestation.
While fighting crimes against women in Delhi, a short-fused policewoman and her level-headed female boss grapple with gender issues in their own lives.
In this true crime documentary, a family falls prey to the manipulative charms of a neighbor, who abducts their adolescent daughter. Twice.
Inspired by real events, this drama follows a trucker jailed after driving five ill-fated travelers across Quetta, and the officer taking on his case.
With the earth alliance weakened, Haruo weighs siding with the Exif, whose death cult is summoning a monster that can destroy the world.
Argentine cuarteto singer Rodrigo "El Potro" Bueno rises to fame amid personal struggles in this dramatization of the charismatic superstar's life.
An aspiring music director begins to receive voyeuristic footage of his girlfriend from her apparent stalker as tragedy strikes those around him.
British comic Gina Yashere takes the stage in San Francisco, where she shares her thoughts on everything from toilet ninjas to her troublesome name.
When street vices keep them coming back, three prisoners make sense of their lives in a penitentiary – and beyond it – through rap.
Taylor Swift takes the stage in Dallas for the reputation Stadium Tour and celebrates a monumental night of music, memories and visual magic.

Titulo: The Seven Deadly Sins the Movie: Prisoners of the Sky
Enredo: The Seven Deadly Sins aid the Sky People against a powerful group of demons hellbent on resurrecting a demonic beast sealed over 3,000 years ago.
Standup star Tim Allen storms the stage for a set chock-full of observations about powerful cars, beautiful lawns and more of the things he loves.

Titulo: Tim Minchin And The Heritage Orchestra Live
Enredo: Flanked by a full orchestra, Tim Minchin takes the Royal Albert Hall by storm with a wonderfully witty evening of satirical musical comedy.
Comedic pianist Tim Minchin performs a host of his catchy songs that touch on everything from the Middle East to the healing power of canvas bags.
Standup comedian Todd Glass gets right down to it, with sly observations on accepting directions, denying compliments and being afraid of the dark.

Titulo: Tom Papa Live in New York City
Enredo: Comedian Tom Papa riffs on the trials of married life, fatherhood in the 21st century, domestic pets and more in his stand-up show.
Future Uruguayan president José Mujica and his fellow Tupamaro political prisoners fight to survive 12 years of solitary confinement and torture.

Titulo: Aggretsuko: We Wish You a Metal Christmas
Enredo: While Retsuko desperately makes plans for Christmas Eve, her new obsession with seeking validation through social media spirals out of control.
The life of a radio talk-show host is turned upside down after a murderous caller dials into her program and asks her to choose his next victim.
Entangling the lives of a movie star, a chauffeur, a prostitute and a pimp, this bold drama reveals ugly truths beneath Mumbai’s glitzy veneer.

Titulo: Prince of Peoria: A Christmas Moose Miracle
Enredo: Teddy's never missed the Festival of Lights, but the bowling alley’s been snowed in! Not to worry – Emil insists the Christmas moose will save the day.

Titulo: Dragons: Dawn of the Dragon Racers
Enredo: The "How to Train Your Dragon" adventure continues when a hunt for lost sheep turns into a fierce, fun-filled competition.
Bruce Springsteen shares personal stories from his life and acoustic versions of some of his best-known songs in an intimate one-man show.
When a tour guide in Japan goes blind after seeing her fiancé’s infidelity, she befriends a fellow Filipino keen to coax her out of the darkness.
Director Alfonso Cuarón delivers a vivid, emotional portrait of domestic life and social hierarchy set against Mexico's political turmoil of the 1970s.
Russell Brand gets loquacious in London as he ruminates on the state of the world and marvels over how his life changed the moment he became a father.

Titulo: Ayotzinapa, el paso de la tortuga
Enredo: Delving into the disappearance of 43 college students in Mexico, this documentary seeks to give justice and a voice to the victims and their families.
In this "Oddbods" special, Bubbles's latest invention, the Naughty-or-Nice Machine, zaps Santa Claus, jeopardizing the whole Christmas holiday season.
Retired, restless and constantly butting heads with his son, a former stuntman escapes on a road trip that becomes a journey to find his first love.
Backed by a crew of unlikely allies, newly sober paraplegic Gabriel Cordell teams up with his nephew for a grueling wheelchair trek across America.
A trip to church with her family on Christmas Eve gives young Angela an extraordinary idea. A heartwarming tale based on a story by Frank McCourt.
An insomniac, an aspiring photographer and a pregnant veterinarian form a unique friendship during late-night meetings at a 24-hour mini-mart.

Titulo: My Little Pony Friendship Is Magic: Best Gift Ever
Enredo: The ponies get in the spirit of the holidays by drawing names for a gift exchange, then race around Equestria in search of the perfect presents.
An executive-turned-viral sensation loses his reputation and his memory, but finds a new life with his biological mother and her empowered dance group.
In 1843, crippled Martin returns from war to his Basque hometown and finds his brother has grown into a giant, which they turn into a circus act.
Bound by a family rule that forbids him from marrying until his stubborn sister gets hitched, a bachelor enlists the help of a love guru to woo her.

Titulo: They’ll Love Me When I’m Dead
Enredo: Actors, crew members and others who were there discuss the tumultuous creation of Orson Welles's final, unfinished film, “The Other Side of the Wind.”
Thrown out of the elite dance studio he founded, Vishnu's spirits rebound when he sees young street dancers prepping for an annual contest.
This animated retelling of the classic Indian tale of Prince Arjun – part of the Sanskrit epic Mahabharata – begins during the prince's youth.
Still reeling from a business failure, the restaurant manager of a ski resort finds her world jolted by a new chef, who has his own hidden past.
An accountant and a producer hatch a scheme to finance a movie, while making every effort to ensure that it flops so they may pocket the difference.

Titulo: Edmilson Filho: Notas, Comedy about Relationships
Enredo: Brazilian comedian Edmilson Filho walks his audience through the stages of a modern relationship, playing up the differences between men and women.
An Indian man who has become a major business mogul in Canada must return to his homeland where he's reviled due to being wrongly branded a traitor.

Titulo: Katt Williams: The Pimp Chronicles: Pt. 1
Enredo: In this 2006 show, comic Katt Williams uses his edgy style and personal experiences to paint a sassy, hilarious portrait of life in black America.
A group of Mumbai up-and-comers search for love and struggle for success in this ensemble drama that centers on an eager young call-center executive.
Paan Singh Tomar goes from celebrated runner to star brigand and rebel when life after sports fails to unfold as planned.
Three youths from rural South Africa set out for Johannesburg, where they're thrust into the seedy underbelly of the city and must fight to survive.
A poor family’s goat suddenly acquires divine status, sparking a widespread frenzy as everyone clamors to benefit from its unexpected celebrity.
Villagers in the kingdom of Mahismati rescue a baby who is destined to embark on a heroic quest in this English version of S.S. Rajamouli's epic.
From "Heroes" to "Ice Cream Ladies" – Adam Sandler's comedy special hits you with new songs and jokes in an unexpected, groundbreaking way.
The Scorpion King joins forces with a Nubian princess in an all-or-nothing fight to stop a warlord from claiming the souls of the vanquished.

Titulo: Club de Cuervos Presents: I, Potro
Enredo: Former Club de Cuervos player Potro returns home to Argentina to crash the wedding of his famous soccer-star brother and confront his estranged family.
Illusionist Derren Brown concocts a psychological experiment in which he tries to manipulate an ordinary person into taking a bullet for a stranger.
After moving into a new house with her mom, high schooler Chloe discovers a troupe of talking garden gnomes who need her help saving the world.
A father leading a dark double life and his daughter, who's eager to pursue her studies in Hyderabad, face the tragic consequences of sex trafficking.
After devastating terror attacks in Norway, a young survivor, grieving families and the country rally for justice and healing. Based on a true story.
Buckle up for an anthology of socially conscious horror stories that focus on the perils of racial injustice and the price of ignorance.
An ex-racecar driver is sent to a barbaric prison where, to get pardoned, he must defeat the inmate known as Frankenstein in a lethal "Death Race."
In a madcap stage play from Monty Python icon Eric Idle, comic greats perform the decline and fall of the British Empire ... as told through a piano.
Follow the evolution of the British sketch comedy troupe that redefined humor and shaped an entire generation of American comics.

Titulo: Monty Python Live (Mostly): One Down, Five to Go
Enredo: Live from London in a sold-out final show, surviving members of the British comedy troupe reprise old roles and break out in irreverent song and dance.

Titulo: Monty Python: Before the Flying Circus
Enredo: Discover how six seemingly ordinary but supremely talented men became Monty Python, sketch comedy's revolutionary comedy troupe.

Titulo: Monty Python: Live at The Hollywood Bowl
Enredo: Film clips and Terry Gilliam animations feature in this live-to-tape performance of greatest hits, including "Travel Agent" and "Solo Wrestling."
Born in a stable in Judea, Brian grows up to join a group of anti-Roman zealots, but his fate keeps getting confused with that of a certain carpenter.

Titulo: Parrot Sketch Not Included: Twenty Years of Monty Python
Enredo: Presented by Steve Martin, this anthology draws from “Flying Circus” and “Fliegender Zirkus” to mark the 20th anniversary of the TV series.
In the ancient walled city of Delhi, an American-born Indian finds himself on an unexpected inner journey as he learns about himself and his roots.

Titulo: My Little Pony Equestria Girls: Forgotten Friendship
Enredo: School yearbook editor Sunset Shimmer has suddenly been erased from the memories of her best friends and must find out how to fix this.

Titulo: My Little Pony Equestria Girls: Rollercoaster of Friendship
Enredo: Rarity gets a summer job at Equestria Land, making Applejack feel jealous. But when their friends start vanishing, they must work together to find them.
Complications around the cremation of their deceased friend inspire three septuagenarian friends to build their own mortuary.
Three old friends who have always hated politics are in for a shock when the friend who dislikes politics the most is somehow elected head minister.
Featuring experts in their fields and raw and moving footage, this documentary makes a case for increased autonomy in women's choices for childbirth.
When shy Kumar gets stuck on the losing end of a love triangle, the Love Doctor, Mokia, has a strategy for Kumar to win the love of his life.
A divorced mother of three children runs a happy household – until her former husband brings his new career-oriented girlfriend into the picture.

Titulo: Lessons from a School Shooting: Notes from Dunblane
Enredo: Two priests – one from Dunblane, Scotland, the other from Newtown, Connecticut – bond over school tragedies that occurred 16 years apart.
When her little sister claims she sees the dead, Alia consults a psychic, who opens her own eyes to the vengeful ghosts haunting their childhood home.
Women who've been sexually brutalized in war-torn Congo begin to heal at City of Joy, a center that helps them regain a sense of self and empowerment.
A wrong-number text sparks a virtual romance between a smart but unpopular teen and a sweet jock who thinks he's talking to a gorgeous cheerleader.
Aamir Khan teams with director Rajkumar Hirani to play a social crusader in a political satire on the state of corruption in India.
On the verge of losing his business, an entrepreneur launches a carbon tax scam that thrusts him into a web of criminals, intrigue and murder.
After accidentally connecting over the Internet, two strangers form a tight friendship – not knowing they already share a bond.
After a chance phone call leads to daily conversations, a widowed restaurant owner and a lonely film actor plan to finally meet in person.

Titulo: Maria Bamford: The Special Special Special
Enredo: Spend an evening with gleeful, oh-so-awkward Maria Bamford via her cozy, shot-at-home comedy special, which has a two-person audience: her parents.
When she falls in love with the author of a novel she adores, bohemian Bitti enlists the help of a local printer to find her new object of affection.
After her stepdaughter is sexually assaulted at a party, a furious mother sets out to destroy the lives of the four perpetrators who walked away free.
On her first day of marriage, a woman leaves her husband upon learning his home lacks a toilet, sparking a quixotic quest to acquire modern sanitation.

Titulo: To All the Boys I’ve Loved Before
Enredo: When her secret love letters somehow get mailed to each of her five crushes, Lara Jean finds her quiet high school existence turned upside down.
A software engineer must decide if he'd rather navigate America's frustrating visa renewal process or simply return to his home country of India.

Titulo: The Guernsey Literary and Potato Peel Pie Society
Enredo: A London writer bonds with the colorful residents of Guernsey as she learns about the book club they formed during the WWII German occupation.
Faking his death to escape the realities of his uneventful life worked out well for Brij Mohan – until he was sentenced to death for his own murder.
Memories in a bowl of steaming noodles, a fading beauty finding her way and a bittersweet first love – all in these stories of city life in China.
A financially troubled Indian man heads to Singapore to find employment, while his pretty wife stays behind in a move that could cause trouble.
Kath and Kel's union is tested by Michael Bublé, daughter Kim tries pole dancing, pal Sharon finds love online, and a stalker lurks amid Yuletide cheer.

Titulo: GODZILLA City on the Edge of Battle
Enredo: On Earth, Haruo and his companions make contact with the indigenous Houtua tribe. To defeat Godzilla, they set out for the old Mechagodzilla facility.

Titulo: Felipe Esparza: They're Not Going to Laugh at You
Enredo: "Last Comic Standing" winner Felipe Esparza runs riot in his first comedy special with his wry comments on life as a wild man from East Los Angeles.
Strapped for cash, a traveling projectionist begins to run a DVD pirating business, putting him at odds with his young, skeptical son.
Left brain and right brain duke it out – and ultimately belt out a melody – in stand-up comedian Bo Burnham's quick and clever one-man show.
During Mexico's War of Independence, a group of men face unimaginable horrors when they attempt to steal from the seemingly helpless Cordero sisters.
DJs and industry insiders offer a backstage pass to the world of electronic dance music, reflecting on its radical origins and the future of the genre.
A drug dealer starts having doubts about his trade as his brother, his client, and two rappers from the slums each battle their own secret addictions.

Titulo: Bill Burr: You People Are All the Same
Enredo: Funnyman Bill Burr takes the stage to uncork a profanity-laced, incisive routine that pokes fun at plastic surgery, reality TV, gold diggers and more.
Kidnapped by an inventor who uses her as a test subject to perfect his robotic AI, a street-smart young woman tries to escape her high-tech prison.
Stricken with seizures, psychosis and memory loss, a young New York Post reporter visits doctor after doctor in search of an elusive diagnosis.
Illusionist Derren Brown reinvents the concept of "faith healing” through a series of stunts that debunk the confines of fear, pain and disbelief.
After surviving a bomb attack, two low-level mobsters in Jerusalem change their ways and set about making strangers' Wailing Wall prayers come true.
Four scientists offer a sweeping yet intimate exploration of Peru's majestic coastline by land, sea and air.
Decades after being abandoned as a young child, Chiara finds her mother and asks her to spend 10 days together in a remote location.
In this compelling true story, two Peruvian detectives go undercover to locate and capture the elusive leader of the Shining Path guerrilla army.
After telling a white lie that spins out of control, the son of an Iraqi-born cleric in Melbourne becomes torn between family duty and his own heart.
Mexican stand-up comedian Franco Escamilla draws his jokes from real-life experiences – and he's willing to do anything for new material.
A young woman eager to avoid an arranged marriage moves to Mumbai, where she learns hard truths about show business, life and love.
Over the course of one memorable and adventure-filled year, Felix Starck documents his 18,000-kilometer bicycle journey across 22 countries.

Titulo: Tig Notaro Happy To Be Here
Enredo: Comedian Tig Notaro unleashes her inner prankster in a playful stand-up special packed with funny anecdotes, parenting confessions and more.
Amid growing tensions in their marriage, a Johannesburg professor and his journalist wife find their lives upended by a famous, hard-partying author.
An aspiring actor leaves Hollywood and takes to the road to do stand-up after he's cast in a series of increasingly stereotypical "black" roles.

Titulo: Lupin the 3rd: The Castle of Cagliostro: Special Edition
Enredo: Lupin, his sidekick, Jigen, and the samurai warrior Goemon set out to take over an evil counterfeit operation at Count Cagliostro's fortress.
Struggling writer Wally Spivak is stuck in a rut – until he meets an engaged couple and starts to see life in a whole new way.
Germany's most celebrated actor is commissioned by Nazi propagandist Joseph Goebbels to prepare the leader of the Third Reich to deliver a speech.

Titulo: Dany Boon: Des Hauts De France
Enredo: In an eclectic one-man show, French superstar Dany Boon reflects on his homeland, his first comedy gig and the challenges of parenting hostile teens.
A Chinese pharmaceutical lawyer framed for a vile crime teams up with a sharp-witted Japanese detective to stop a dangerous corporate plot.
Along with her two friends, a determined woman travels to Vietnam to bring home the baby her recently deceased daughter had planned to adopt.

Titulo: Si saben cómo me pongo ¿pá qué me invitan?
Enredo: When four unhappy couples attend a spiritual retreat at a resort to try and solve their relationship troubles, shenanigans ensue.
A young man in Kerala has two weeks to stop the woman he loves from a fixed marriage in the U.S., but he doesn't have the papers to get there.
A Spaniard working in Argentina sees his life upended after accidentally giving bad directions to a passerby, who demands compensation for the error.
Pocoyo gears up for exciting car races and learns that friends, teamwork and imagination are what matter the most.
Acrobatic aliens arrive on spaceships and perform for everyone, but when angry aliens arrive as well, Pocoyo and his friends must now put on a show.
To celebrate the carnival, everyone learns to dance to different music. Plus, Pocoyo's friends surprise him with something delicious.
Pocoyo and his friends have a costume contest to celebrate Halloween and learn new things about planets and stars in space.
Pocoyo finds a special toy and plays new games with his friends, then they’re spooked by a scary box and try to find out who’s inside.
Everyone is getting excited for the games. Pocoyo plays baseball and golf, and races with his friends. Ready, set, go!
Seven strangers anxiously waiting for their HIV test results decide to bribe the clinic receptionist to get them early, learning one is positive.
A newcomer ekes out a living in LA as a professional audience member on infomercials, but life gets complicated when he's thrust into the spotlight.
A young priest coaches a team of uncoordinated monks in order to win a soccer tournament and save their monastery from being turned into a hotel.
A record company exec joins his estranged dad, a famous photographer who's dying, on a road trip to the last lab still developing Kodachrome film.
A Brazilian man tries a myriad of ways to get over his breakup with his girlfriend but is surprised to learn it's more difficult than he anticipated.

Titulo: I Am not an Easy Man
Enredo: A shameless chauvinist gets a taste of his own medicine when he wakes up in a world dominated by women and locks horns with a powerful female author.
Aspiring teen thieves learn what it takes to be successful pickpockets on the streets of Bogotá from a master in the arts of trickery and deception.
From his home on Maui, pioneering researcher, author and spiritual teacher Ram Dass reflects on love, life and death as his own days draw to a close.
A former medical student battles for survival against an evil human-zombie hybrid determined to destroy her, in this reimagining of the 1985 classic.

Titulo: Sofía Niño de Rivera: Selección Natural
Enredo: Mexico's Sofía Niño de Rivera brings her dark humor to the stage with jokes about marriage traps, sexually attractive leopards and funny funerals.
A sheltered farm girl inadvertently shoots an endangered Philippine eagle, setting off a police investigation that exposes violence and corruption.
Neil Young and his band of outlaws sow seeds of strange mischief and musical wonder under Western skies in this dreamlike film by Daryl Hannah.
She grew up in a tough New York neighborhood in the '80s and made history with "Roxanne's Revenge." The story of teen battle rap champ Roxanne Shante.
Tired of her passionless marriage, Marianne wants a separation from her husband, Gustav, who, in response, decides to make a big change of his own.
During Communist rule, a Polish gynecologist and sexologist defies taboo and fights to publish her groundbreaking book on love and sex.
Amid a coup, a North Korean agent escapes south with the country's injured leader in an attempt to keep him alive and prevent a Korean war.
Born amid poverty and limited women's rights in the village of Ratu, India, Deepika Kumari rose to become the No.1 female archer in the world at 18.
A radio broadcaster's intense attraction to a mysterious woman opens the door to a tidal wave of powerful emotions and desires.
After enrolling in a college poetry course, a struggling rapper finds inspiration for her new voice through slam poetry.
The last of his family line, Olaf Schubert doesn't have time for a girlfriend but dutifully searches for one when his father demands offspring.

Titulo: Trailer Park Boys Live at the North Pole
Enredo: Bubbles's plan to spread the true meaning of Christmas is dashed by Julian's wish to cash in on the holiday and Ricky's quest to meet the real Santa.

Titulo: Trailer Park Boys Live In F**kin' Dublin
Enredo: The boys head to Ireland after winning a contest to see Rush but are arrested by immigration and must perform a community service puppet show.
See what Sunnyvale Trailer Park was like back in the day, featuring Randy as a prostitute, J-Roc before he rapped and Barb and Lahey still together.
When their Sunday soccer game on the beach is canceled, five friends set out to find another place to play in the noisy, crowded city of Mumbai.
After people in his town start turning up dead, a grumpy landlord is visited by a man who recounts an unsolved serial murder case from 30 years ago.
Mentalist Derren Brown engineers an audacious social experiment demonstrating how manipulation can lead an ordinary person to commit an appalling act.
While alchemist Edward Elric searches for a way to restore his brother Al's body, the military government and mysterious monsters are watching closely.
Individually, bank employees Sanjay and Karina don't earn enough to be able to buy a home, so they decide to enter into a marriage of convenience.
