Twentysomething Georgia pines for her old boyfriend and is thrilled to have a second chance at love when she attends their high school reunion.
In the Smoky Mountains, an ambitious woman works to save her family's historic berry farm as her ex, a country music star, returns to town.
When Luther Krank and his wife opt to skip Christmas – no tree and no rooftop Frosty – can they handle the fallout from their family and neighbors?
Soccer goalie Claudio Tamburrini is kidnapped by the Argentine military. Several months later, he joins other prisoners in planning a daring escape.
The lives of five hapless, petty criminals careen into madcap disarray when their plan to abduct a wealthy minister’s son goes horribly wrong.
Jealous of the high regard in which his new wife holds their brother-in-law, a botany professor stages an elaborate prank that will even the score.

Titulo: Cirque du Freak: The Vampire's Assistant
Enredo: When Darren Shan is taken to a circus that's chock-full of sideshow oddities, he meets a vampire and receives a life-changing bite on the neck.
Growing up in a Rio de Janeiro slum, Rocket is able to avoid being drawn into a life of drugs and crime by having a passion for photography.
In moody London, a burned-out sleuth sinks into a world of corruption and murderous romance when he tackles a mysterious case of a missing sex worker.

Titulo: Clarence Clemons: Who Do I Think I Am?
Enredo: This intimate documentary follows the life of legendary saxophonist Clarence Clemons and his spiritual awakening before his death in 2011.
If he is to save the life of the beautiful Princess Andromeda, the valiant Perseus must battle a host of powerful, beastly enemies.
As the Civil War looms, a runaway slave seeks freedom, and West Point cadets find their camaraderie shattered as they choose between North or South.
When her class rank threatens her college plans, an ambitious teen convinces a nerdy peer to run for the school board to abolish the ranking system.
A stylin' special agent chases down drug lords and does her part to stop trafficking. Soon, she finds herself seeking revenge on a dealer.
Overworked Michael Newman stumbles on a universal remote control that gives him the power to pause or fast-forward through scenes in his life.
Martin and Claudia, top-flight lawyers who happen to be former lovers, become targets when they're teamed up to defend a notorious terrorist.
In this star-studded drama, six seemingly disparate stories explore the complicated links that humanity shares through the generations.
A middle-aged actress is cast in a film adaptation of the play that made her famous 20 years earlier, but in a much less glamorous role.
A going-away party in Manhattan is interrupted when a mysterious monster of epic proportions launches an attack on New York City.
Controversial basketball coach Ken Carter puts school before sports and benches his undefeated high school team for poor academic performance.
A mild-mannered janitor duped into believing he's an undercover agent stumbles into an international arms ring plot involving the CIA and the FBI.
Low TV ratings drive a well-known journalist to concoct a plan to interview a notorious underworld figure who is also a suspected terrorist.
When Christopher Columbus mysteriously appears in modern-day Kolkata, India, two struggling young men look to him for advice on achieving success.
When her boyfriend is caught up in a Chilean coup, a young woman tries to free him from a prison camp posing as a commune by joining it voluntarily.
Seeking inspiration, a young 19th-century painter finds a woman who is his love, his muse and his willing subject, but his work becomes controversial.
When his photographer girlfriend vanishes, an L.A. graphic designer starts his own investigation and uncovers a web of deceit, crime and corruption.
Chronicling a 1980 Titan II missile accident, this sobering documentary weighs the balance of power and safety involving weapons of mass destruction.
Following a misunderstanding, a gangster and his boss part ways and become bitter enemies – with devastating consequences.
Lured to a majestic, remote villa by an old lover, an erotic novelist finds herself falling for a mysterious woman and descending into a moral abyss.
The development of professional soccer worldwide owes a great debt to the soccer – or "football" – that is played on the streets of France.
A lesbian housewife, feeling trapped in a stale marriage, begins visiting female prostitutes and soon seeks excitement by becoming a sex worker.
In the wake of her husband's betrayal, a novelist and mother moves to an old building, where she receives a music box and encounters a strange spirit.
From making ends meet to lavish rides and fur coats, the Irish MMA champion grants an all-access pass to the highs – and lows – of his ascent.
Secrets bubble to the surface after a sensual encounter and an unforeseen crime entangle two friends and a woman caught between them.
Following the death of his wife and daughter in a terrorist attack, an ex-Indian army commando agrees to infiltrate a terrorist cell.
Sentenced to death for committing rape, a convict navigates his final trying days alongside his allies and enemies in prison.
Luke Jackson likes to do things his own way, which leads to a world of hurt when he ends up in a prison camp – and on the wrong side of its warden.

Titulo: Cop and a Half: New Recruit
Enredo: A world-weary detective is forced to team up with a 12-year-old who thinks she's a cop in order to solve a case that's baffled police.
Curious young Coraline unlocks a door in her family's home and is transported to a universe that strangely resembles her own – only better.
Two teenagers print counterfeit money in their high school art room, but things go terribly wrong when their debt-ridden teacher becomes suspicious.
Christian musician Israel Houghton leads his band Israel & New Breed on a tour supporting their newest album of multicultural, hybrid-genre songs.
In post-Sept. 11 Los Angeles, tensions erupt when the lives of people from all walks of life converge during a 36-hour period.
At odds with his radical instructor's ruthless methods, a drama student assembles his own troupe of misfit actors ahead of a prestigious competition.
A young woman in ancient China longs for an adventurous life rather than a dull arranged marriage in Ang Lee's Oscar-winning martial arts epic.
Following a string of murders in the asylum where she's confined, Nica Pierce begins to wonder whether Chucky is real after all.
A 2014 Oscar nominee for Best Documentary Feature, this film explores the symbiotic relationship of artists Ushio and Noriko Shinohara.
A simple man's peaceful life is complicated when an incident brings him in contact with a gangster and launches his journey into the underworld.
A cardiologist tries to pinpoint the cause of her mother's sudden death as her sister, who witnessed it, claims malevolent demons are at play.
Family bonds are revived after a father is diagnosed with cancer in this bittersweet drama. Dutiful son John cares for his aging father, Jake, but not without complaint.
When a conscientious father loses his lucrative dot-com job and faces economic ruin, he joins two friends in opening a business called Daddy Day Care.
Maya finally hooks up with her online dream girl, only to discover she’s deeply involved with an older sugar daddy – a man Maya knows all too well.
In a realm where magic and technology intersect, a shifty, cigar-smoking wizard finds himself in the middle of a war with the powers of hell.
A retired government worker continues to dedicate himself to public service, but his principled ways soon clash with those of his extravagant sons.
A lesbian daughter fights off an arranged marriage in India while an Islamic fundamentalist targets an anti-extremist Muslim scholar in New York.
Refusing to accept a death sentence from his doctor after being diagnosed with AIDS in 1986, Ron Woodroof smuggles medications from abroad.
In this adaptation of the TV series, Tara recovers from injury and pursues a career in the U.S., where she grapples with love and professional rejection.
After years of battling a deep depression, a young woman attempts to pass an important exam with the help of a fellow student.
This documentary profiles eccentric publicist Danny Fields, who helped launch the careers of innovative new artists who would become musical icons.
When a volcanologist comes to investigate the recent rumblings of a dormant volcano, a massive eruption has everyone in town fighting for their lives.
Irish landscape designer Mary Reynolds fights to bring her wild and unconventional style to the esteemed Chelsea Flower Show.
In this Bangla thriller inspired by a true story, the discovery of a charred corpse in the woods leads to a high-profile murder investigation.
A detective on a cold murder case discovers that a famous writer’s latest novel contains details chillingly similar to the crime he’s investigating.
Years after surviving a brutal crime as a child, Libby Day comes to believe that the brother she testified against for committing it may be innocent.
Stranded in a jungle when their car breaks down, six friends pass their time exchanging horror stories, unaware that they may be part of one themselves.
An African American Gullah family leaves their coastal island home in 1902 and risks losing their culture to start a new life on the U.S. mainland.
Following the shooting death of his older brother, a depressed and aimless 13-year-old boy falls in with a gang in rural Arkansas.
A YouTuber becomes obsessed with figuring out how his copycat archnemesis manages to steal all of his ideas.
Iconoclastic film director Brian DePalma takes a look back at the production of such classic movies as "Carrie," "Scarface" and "The Untouchables."

Titulo: Dead in a Week (Or Your Money Back)
Enredo: After several failed attempts at taking his own life, a young man hires an aging assassin who’ll do anything to fend off retirement.
A surgeon’s perfect life is rattled when his daughter is taken hostage in their own home and he's given 24 hours to pay a hefty ransom.
After a series of strange deaths, a high school reporter tries to pin down the killer who's targeting students eligible for a prestigious scholarship.
As his father takes steps to move on, a New Yorker grieving his mom's death visits Los Angeles where new possibilities may bring him out of his funk.
A father and son bond on an impromptu road trip over deep conversations, unexpected confessions, strange encounters ... and a drunken escapade.
When he gets a fan letter from a young monster movie buff, Dracula visits him and soon has a new friend helping him to get his confidence back.
Finding a letter mailed to Santa by a girl asking for a new wife for her daddy, twentysomething Crystal sets out to make the girl's wishes come true.
When a Los Angeles family's patriarch dies, his dutiful eldest son plans the funeral – which becomes a fiasco thanks to a colorful cast of attendees.
Two federal agents battle through an army of rioting prisoners – and their sense of reality – inside a high-tech prison modeled after Dante’s Inferno.
Mountain bikers – including legend Brendan Fairclough – put their skills to the test and engage in daring feats set against vivid backdrops.
Hired by a singer to defend her friend, who has been accused of murder, a formidable lawyer learns that the man he represents may not be innocent.

Titulo: Defying the Nazis: The Sharps' War
Enredo: This film documents the story of minister Waitstill Sharp and his wife, Martha, who risked everything to save thousands of refugees fleeing the Nazis.
After Zimbabwe's disputed 2008 election results, political enemies are asked to write a new constitution and save their country from a bleak future.
A highly skilled crew of bank robbers plotting a heist at the supposedly impenetrable Federal Reserve faces off against an elite unit of L.A. cops.

Titulo: Denis Leary: No Cure For Cancer
Enredo: In the stand-up performance that made him a legend, comedian Denis Leary caustically holds forth on nonsmokers, vegetarians and other undesirables.
In a severe, drought-ravaged dystopia, the youngest of a farm family starts a quest for revenge after his brothers betray him and leave him for dead.
Along with her son and best friend, a grieving widow hikes into the woods to scatter her late husband's ashes, only to discover they're being stalked.
A man begins to regret his choices when his brother decides to join him as a member of the same terrorist organization.
Convinced his stepfather caused the crash that left his mother in a coma, a law student drunkenly agrees to his murder, then can't rescind the deal.
On a small Finnish island in 1666, a teenage girl in love with a married fisherman becomes the center of a tragic witch hunt and power struggle.
Seeking a missing woman in North Dakota, an FBI agent and a sheriff focus on her religious zealot husband but discover something far more sinister.
After science student Shesh Shahi – a shy eccentric with a strange connection to nature – is examined by a team of mental hospital doctors, a gripping portrait of schizophrenia emerges.
Framed by an empress who plans to steal a dragon-taming mace, imperial magistrate Dee Renjie soon uncovers a greater plot that threatens the kingdom.

Titulo: Diana: 7 Days That Shook the World
Enredo: This illuminating documentary examines the aftermath of Princess Diana’s tragic death and the tense, dramatic week leading up to her funeral.
Featuring archival footage and personal recordings, this documentary offers candid insight into the life of the beloved princess.
An attractive young woman goes to work as a chambermaid for a troublesome couple. The wife is unreasonable, and the husband won't stop hitting on her.
Pierce Brosnan's final outing as 007 finds James Bond facing off against a North Korean terrorist who's in league with a British diamond merchant.
The sophisticated son of a powerful businessman falls for a simple, free-spirited girl whose older sister is in love with him.
The host of a dinner party invites his friends to bring the saddest loser they can find. But the ultimate schmuck turns everyone else into the losers.
Shaolin monk San Te returns to protect a fellow hero with a talent for finding trouble in this action-packed sequel to "The 36th Chamber of Shaolin."
Follow Todd Standing, Dr. Jeff Meldrum and other researchers into the wilderness, where they try to capture definitive proof of Sasquatch's existence.
After years of segregation and forced labor, a race of stranded aliens enlists in a resistance movement spearheaded by a rogue government agent.
A young physician and his beautiful mistress get swept up in the danger and drama of the Bolshevik Revolution in this Oscar-winning epic.
A delusional ex-con rejoins his unhinged former partners for one last job: kidnap the baby of a mobster's enemy for ransom.
After losing his mom, 10-year-old Luke abandons competitive swimming. It takes a friendly dolphin to get him back in the water – and help him heal.
Winter the dolphin, who survived a tragic injury by receiving a prosthetic tail, bonds with an orphaned baby dolphin after her beloved pool mate dies.

Titulo: Don Quixote: The Ingenious Gentleman of La Mancha
Enredo: In this modern adaptation of a Spanish classic, an eccentric, elderly gentleman sets out with his honest sidekick to right the wrongs of the world.
A questionable character working as a self-styled "biblical archaeologist" advances his cause by creating phony religious artifacts.

Titulo: Don't Be Afraid of the Dark
Enredo: Young Sally Hurst discovers she isn't alone in her new house: strange creatures live there – and they might not be as friendly as Sally thinks.
There are risks. Then there are risk-takers. In an around-the-world trip, follow athletes perform jaw-dropping acts in unpredictable elements of nature.
Using state-of-the-art technology, this stunning sequel follows athletes pulling off daring feats under extreme conditions in extraordinary locations.
Through deserts, above mountains and deep into oceans, elite athletes — both veteran and new — form bonds and pursue adventure in sumptuous landscapes.
A recovering addict becomes her estranged daughter's only hope after the teen awakens a terrifying child-stealing witch from an urban legend.
When FBI agent Joe Pistone goes undercover to infiltrate the mob, he starts to identify with the made men he's charged with taking down.
A special ops squad investigating a distress signal from a distant planet discovers that mutant aliens have already wiped out most of the population.
Sister Aloysius begins to have doubts about doting Father Flynn, who seems to have become overly involved in the life of an African American pupil.
The human-equine bond propels the unique and challenging sport of reined cow horse, in which dedicated trainers compete for the national championship.

Titulo: Dr. Seuss' The Cat in the Hat
Enredo: While Mom is away, a bored little boy and girl are visited by the Cat in the Hat, who proceeds to turn the house into the "mother of all messes."
A grump with a mean streak plots to bring Christmas to a halt in the cheerful town of Whoville. But a generous little girl could change his heart.
In ancient times when majestic fire-breathers soared through the skies, a knight comes face to face and heart to heart with the last dragon on Earth.
When an aspiring knight crosses paths with a dragon, the two form an unlikely alliance in a high-stakes battle against a malicious sorcerer.
This sequel introduces Draco the dragon's offspring, Drake, who dreams of becoming a knight and teams up with a stable boy to master his skills.
Bheem helps to reopen Dragonpur's abandoned magic and martial arts school, but is tested like never before when an ex-student returns seeking revenge!
Narrated by Jeff Bridges, this compelling documentary examines some incredible achievements of engineering from across the globe.
On a cruise for gay men, five passengers of different nationalities take a break from their families and cultures to party and reflect on life.
This documentary explores the intense passion and distinctive talent that make Dries Van Noten one of the most unique fashion designers in the world.
A young dancer grapples with her dream to join a famed ballet company against the wishes of her mother, who pushes her to pursue a more practical path.
When one of his colleagues becomes corrupted by power and goes over to the dark side, a young police officer tries to bring the offender to justice.

Titulo: Dumb and Dumberer: When Harry Met Lloyd
Enredo: This wacky prequel to the 1994 blockbuster goes back to the lame-brained title characters' days as classmates at a Rhode Island high school.
This documentary investigates the surge in vaping culture and whether e-cigarettes can really help smokers kick the habit.
When a construction project begins in their neighborhood, four friends start receiving bizarre encoded text messages on their cell phones.
She’s not the usual candidate for the role, but a dogged Mexican-American mother makes it her mission to become a talented sushi chef.
When a lie about Olive's reputation transforms her from anonymous to infamous at her high school, she decides to embrace a provocative new persona.
Flashing the wild stand-up comedy that made him a household name, Eddie Murphy unleashes uncensored observations and parodies in this 1983 live show.
A poor bus conductor's efforts at obtaining information about his enormous electricity bill are hindered by a corrupt system.
Imprisoned for underworld crimes she didn’t commit, a vengeful woman breaks free and goes scorched earth on the smooth-talking suitor who framed her.
A security expert and ex-CIA agent living in Belgium must go on the run with his estranged teen daughter when they're both marked for assassination.
Spanish-Mexican writer Paco Ignacio Taibo II hits the road to trace the footsteps of Ernesto "Che" Guevara and sheds new light on the revolutionary.
This documentary chronicles the decade-long process that led to the end of the ETA, a Basque terrorist group that operated for more than 50 years.
Popular South American bands Márama and Rombai share footage of behind-the-scenes antics and discuss their sudden rise to stardom.
Friends Proog and Emo live in a capricious, seemingly infinite machine with a sinister purpose in this experimental computer-animated short.
A blend of the royal family's intimate recollections and rarely seen home movies pays tribute to Queen Elizabeth II on the eve of her 90th birthday.
When a young newlywed enters the one chamber in her husband’s mansion that’s off-limits, she faces the horrifying consequences of defying the rules.
Trace the overlapping journeys of exceptional women swept up in World War I and hear their tales of bravery on history's front lines.
Mothers, nurses, soldiers and deportees – these women fought against persecution for freedom and survival amid the turbulence of World War II.
From Asia, Africa and Latin America, five women share extraordinary stories of strength and determination in the face of violence and inequality.
Then and now footage of bit players who appeared in "Star Wars" tells the story of how the film and its legions of fans changed their lives forever.
A suburban couple hires a new sitter to watch their three kids for the night, unaware that the young woman isn't who she claims to be.
In 1950s Makassar, the life of a devoted mother is upended when another woman enters her husband's life.
Expelled from private school for attempted suicide, emo Ethan enters the world of Seymour High and meets a cute Christian who's ready to convert him.
This documentary explores the extent to which our sense of smell directs our survival instincts and enriches our sensual experiences.
Warehouse workers Vince and Zack compete in a full-on war to be named Employee of the Month and win a date with their dream girl.
After accidentally killing a young mobster, a guilt-stricken police officer searches for the parents who never came forward to claim their son's body.
Officers Taylor and Zavala patrol the streets of South Central Los Angeles, an area of the city ruled by gangs and riddled with drug violence.
When a humdrum academic spots his double in a movie, he launches a search that leads him to a small-time actor who looks exactly like him.
This documentary digs deep to recount the saga of the superstar self-help guru convicted of negligent homicide in the deaths of three followers.
After his ailing father makes a shocking confession, a desperately depressed man sets out to find the woman he believes will change his destiny.
Recruited by a British agent, Shaolin master Lee infiltrates a remote island and a brutal martial arts tournament to spy on a sinister crime lord.
Two young lovers depart from the norm simply by having romantic feelings for each other in a society where humans have been relieved of all emotions.
In a dystopian future, a totalitarian regime maintains peace by subduing the populace with a drug, and displays of emotion are punishable by death.
Artistic rebellion ignites at the movies when film characters suddenly speak freely to the audience, prompting a surly censor to combat the uprising.
Cora has three sons and a daughter and she´s almost 80. One day during a family reunion the big question comes up: who will be her heir?
An ill and addled man recalls what seems to be a brief but powerful past romance with a kindred spirit, a young Russian woman who lived a lonely life.
While investigating a brutal string of deaths, a detective begins to suspect that mind control may have played a part in the murders.
God summons narcissistic Evan to build an ark in preparation for a flood. Meanwhile, Evan's family interprets his new hobby as a midlife crisis.
After a signal is received from a long-missing spaceship, a rescue ship investigates, but the crew soon realizes something unimaginable has happened.
After a paramedic’s violent death during a weekend trip, his spirit inhabits his friends’ bodies in an effort to save them from a similar fate.
Journeying back to her small Spanish hometown for her sister's wedding, Laura must grapple with long-buried secrets when her daughter is abducted.
After two community college geology professors discover microscopic alien life-forms on a meteorite, the military and government become involved.
A coder at a tech company wins a week-long retreat at the compound of his company's CEO, where he's tasked with testing a new artificial intelligence.
When terrorists hijack a 747 and turn it into a nerve gas bomb aimed at Washington, D.C., commandos use an experimental plane to try to stop them.
Featuring interviews with participants on all sides, this documentary questions Norway and the West's protracted military involvement in Afghanistan.
When James's living situation turns sour, he has little choice but to move in with his new girlfriend – a decision he almost immediately regrets.
Maverick cop Orin Boyd joins forces with an unlikely ally in gangster Latrell Walker to take down a group of dirty Detroit cops.
Mistakenly accused of kidnapping, a veteran soldier leaves a trail of broken bad guys in his wake as he tries to rescue a teen sex trafficking victim.
A clarinet player who lives with his grandparents in a small village is forced to move to Istanbul, where he meets a singer enjoying sudden fame.
Hüseyin has found his father, and now has one more mission – to get together with the girl of his dreams, with a little help from his new friend.
Life is tough for Hüseyin after marrying his true love. He works day and night to support his growing family, while singer Firuzan copes with fame.
Maddy and Cole were inseparable before high school. Then she got popular; he didn't. But after Maddy is betrayed, she and Cole reunite – to ruin prom.
A young man enlists the help of his friends to avenge his uncle's death by taking on a powerful, unscrupulous politician.
Following a night of hard partying that left their tycoon boss dead, four women try to keep it a secret in hopes of closing a billion-dollar deal.
A tough homicide cop faces his most dangerous assignment when he must stop a murderous evil spirit who can move from one host to the next.
An ex-con struggles to take care of his two brothers, a gambling addict and a young man with Down syndrome, after being released from prison.
Follow an 11-year-old boy as he goes from ordinary child to colorful competitor in his quest for a big win at India’s biggest kite-flying festival.
When a successful young rap star has an affair with an obsessive fan, his life is turned upside down when she kidnaps him.
Spunky, lower-caste lad Jabya falls for lovely, upper-caste Shalu. But his family's derided social position proves a stubborn stumbling block to love.
A beauty expert, a drug dealer and a bungling revolutionary end up in the grips of an extremist group after meeting on a plane to Lebanon.

Titulo: Fear and Loathing in Las Vegas
Enredo: A sportswriter and his Samoan lawyer embark on a hallucinogenic three-day romp from Los Angeles to Las Vegas in this counterculture cult favorite.
Talking squarely to the hip-hop generation, musicians, athletes and others outline the benefits of exercise, a healthy diet and spiritual wellness.
This adaptation of the musical chronicles the trials of a Jewish peasant, his wife, and their three strong-willed daughters in pre-revolutionary Russia.
In Lagos, Nigeria, four successful women on the verge of 50 take stock of their lives and loves over the course of one week.
Quirky little Figaro has a whole alphabet's worth of phobias. These wordless animated shorts follow his many fears from A to Z.
In this documentary, passionate high schoolers travel the country and come of age during a turbulent yearlong prep for a national speech competition.
Leon Vitali had a thriving acting career most others would envy. Then he gave it all up to devote himself completely to the vision of Stanley Kubrick.
The level-headed owner of a struggling coffee shop finds his future at risk when his partner – a talented but cocky barista – makes a major bet.
After narrowly avoiding a fatal plane explosion, a group of seemingly lucky teen classmates finds that Death is not so easily cheated.
On a road trip with friends, Kimberly has a premonition that saves everyone from a freak accident. More terrifying visions prompt her to seek help.
When a girl prevents her premonition of a deadly roller-coaster mishap from coming true, the survivors must face the consequences of cheating death.
Heartbreak, hope and nostalgia collide in this complex portrait of Lampedusa, a Mediterranean island where thousands of migrants land each year.
Grappling with love and loss in their respective lives, two estranged brothers must confront their traumatic, unresolved past when they cross paths.
Unaware they’ve matched online, a struggling writer embellishes his lifestyle to impress a successful exec with whom he sparks an unexpected romance.
A young couple fights supernatural foes in an attempt to save their daughter from the dark and mysterious forces that follow her every move.
In this exploration of the life-changing power of the ocean, six people from very different backgrounds find purpose and meaning in the sea.
Harry Dean Stanton narrates this documentary that follows two modern-day cowboys as they welcome new calves at Montana's Fishtail Basin Ranch.
Top athletes from around the globe test their fitness in a four-day competition at the first-ever CrossFit Sanctional event. Let the games begin.
When five ninjas whose fighting styles are based on natural elements unleash their fury on a rival school, a lone survivor vows deadly revenge.
A college professor goes up against the giants of the auto industry when they fail to give him credit for inventing intermittent windshield wipers.
Nosy family in tow, a fun-loving bachelor goes on a romantic getaway, but he ends up pretending to be married to a complete stranger to avoid trouble.
One night in 1959, four young musicians venture from Pasadena to South-Central Los Angeles in the hopes of hearing a living jazz legend play.
The emperor's reign of terror expands. Heroic outlaw Ma Teng joins a squad of female rebels, whose leader is torn between family loyalties.
Aspiring to be an internet celebrity and make big bucks, a filmmaker travels the world to learn the tricks of the trade from social media influencers.

Titulo: Footprints: The Path of Your Life
Enredo: This documentary follows 10 men who agree to walk the Camino de Santiago, a 500-mile, 40-day trek that will challenge their strength and faith.
This adaptation of Ntozake Shange's play consists of a series of poetic vignettes that explore the lives of modern African American women.
As chef Curtis Duffy oversees every aspect of opening his own restaurant, Grace, he recalls his turbulent childhood and difficult adult relationships.
When a vicious war against Catholics is waged in Mexico in the 1920s, a retired general joins the militia fighting to preserve religious freedom.
When a goofy but likable millionaire discovers his fiancée’s plan to steal his wealth, he devises an unromantic scheme to make her life a living hell.
Benji and his owner get separated in Greece. On his quest to find them, he's targeted by various bad guys who want to get their hands on him.

Titulo: Forbidden Games: The Justin Fashanu Story
Enredo: This documentary chronicles the tragic, true story of Justin Fashanu, the first – and only – openly gay man to have played professional soccer.
A pulp-fiction sci-fi classic, Forbidden Planet stars Leslie Nielsen as a heroic starship captain who finds the paradise planet Altair-IV.
The furor over the addition of two Muslim players to the Beitar Jerusalem soccer club underscores the role of institutionalized racism in Israel.
According to the research of two food scientists, the popularity of processed foods has led to epidemic rates of obesity, diabetes and other diseases.
A commitment-phobic Brit tries to reconnect with an alluring American who's about to make a seemingly awful mistake by marrying a wealthy, boring man.
Ted Crawford, who allegedly attempted to murder his wife, is now locked in a battle of wits with a young assistant district attorney.
Determined to make it as a modern dancer in New York, a young woman pursues her unlikely goal with more enthusiasm than natural talent.
Ordered to clean up the graffiti he painted at a marine theme park, a troubled young boy unexpectedly bonds with a killer whale on exhibit.
Take in the true account of drug kingpin "Freeway" Rick Ross's empire and how the CIA helped him fuel America's  devastating crack cocaine epidemic.
When climate change makes Egypt freeze over, intelligence officers pose as a film crew on location to seek a device that can eliminate the frost.
An aimless, unemployed millennial hangs out with his pals and resists growing up, until an affair with his best friend's girl forces him to change.
A group of teenage camp counselors raises the ire of Jason Voorhees, a masked, homicidal maniac, in this remake of the classic slasher flick.
A popular college student's love of social media becomes her biggest regret when a mysterious account marks each of her friends for a grisly demise.
After his wife relocates to her home country of Japan, an Egyptian man – and father of two rambunctious kids – tries to win her back.

Titulo: Froning: The Fittest Man in History
Enredo: Follow the grueling training regimen of Rich Froning Jr. as he sets his sights on winning an unprecedented fourth CrossFit Games title.
David Attenborough journeys to both polar regions to investigate what rising temperatures will mean for the people and wildlife that live there.
Collecting highlights from the epic documentary series that explores the entire polar year and the inhabitants, from the north to the south.
This documentary explores the challenging, transformative world of high-intensity fitness programs through the eyes of the people who've embraced them.
Kyle helps people disappear, but when a crazed killer starts hunting down his latest client, he has to decide what he's willing to do to keep her safe.
In a drama based on a true story, Brazilian backpacker Gabriel Buchmann spends his gap year exploring Africa. Why does he die in the Malawi mountains?
This biopic of Russian cosmonaut Yuri Gagarin follows his rise from childhood poverty to his selection and training for the 1961 Vostok mission.
Sparks fly between the new girl at school and the misfit with a passion for music. Yet the world threatens to put a stop to their innocent love song.
In the crime-ridden slums of New York in the 1860s, vengeful orphan Amsterdam Vallon joins the cutthroat gang of his father's killer, Bill the Butcher.
A determined boy will do anything to become a great soccer player, despite the wishes of his grandfather.
A young soccer player sets out to prove he can lead his team to a championship – but being a winner is about more than just talent.
Despite growing up with traits that set her apart from her peers, a young adopted girl discovers her gift when she takes an interest in spelling bees.
Ambitious young record company intern Aaron must escort an unruly rock star to Los Angeles for the start of his anniversary concert.
When Santa gets arrested for trespassing after crashing his sleigh, it's up to a father-son team to spring him from jail and save Christmas.
When the identities of secret agents are compromised, hapless Maxwell Smart teams with far more capable Agent 99 to thwart an evil terrorist group.
Tired of dealing with boyfriends who wrong them, gal pals Lauren, Emily and Andrea decide to turn the tables and become the players themselves.
Framed for his older brother's murder, a boxer seeks violent revenge against the true killer who's torn his family apart.
World War IV is over, but a bomb has gone off in Newport City, killing a major arms dealer who may have ties with the mysterious 501 Organization.
After selling his soul to save a loved one, daredevil biker Johnny Blaze pays the price by becoming a flame-skulled bounty hunter for Mephistopheles.
As Motoko and Batou attempt to thwart a mysterious terrorist group, Togusa tracks the killer of a man with a prosthetic leg made by Mermaid's Leg.
Freed of her responsibilities for the 501 Organization, Motoko must now learn how to take orders from Aramaki.
Giving up his life of crime for love, a gangster struggles with a moral dilemma when tragic events and enduring enemies take him back to the underworld.
Indonesian activist Soe Hok Gie experiences a political awakening during the tumultuous regimes of Suharto and Sukarno. Inspired by true events.
Gigi's an avant-garde French waif being groomed as the fille de joie of affluent and handsome Gaston. Soon Gigi metamorphoses into a stunning beauty.
With the Cold War looming over them, teen best pals Ginger and Rosa share everything in early 1960s London – until betrayal drives them apart.
Quadruplets separated as babies reunite in Manila when one needs a liver transplant, but long-held family resentments threaten to derail everything.

Titulo: GLOW: The Story of the Gorgeous Ladies of Wrestling
Enredo: This engaging documentary chronicles the 1980s phenomenon "The Gorgeous Ladies of Wrestling," which elevated its female grapplers to star status.
Through diary entries, this documentary follows the life and death of homeless woman Linda Bishop and her struggles with starvation, sanity and God.
A maverick leader and a clever young general take on Japanese pirates amid bureaucratic intrigue in Ming Dynasty China.
A spiritual college student clashes with an atheistic professor who insists that students will only pass his class by admitting that God is dead.

Titulo: God's Not Dead: A Light in Darkness
Enredo: After a fire breaks out at his church, a pastor faces a legal battle against university leaders who wish to push the congregation off the campus.
When circumstances at work compel Ram to pretend to have a twin, his lie works – until the boss wants his daughter to marry Ram’s fictitious brother.
In the 1980s, a recently discarded television set from the 1960s refuses to accept its fate and tries to break out of the junkyard.
Pierce Brosnan takes his first turn as debonair secret agent James Bond, who investigates the destruction of a Russian satellite weapons base.
When a bold teen mounts a gritty pursuit to dance in a music video, she must also evade child services so she can keep her younger sisters together.
Between thwarting crooks and wooing the belle next door, four pranksters get in over their heads when they bamboozle their way into a couple’s bungalow.
As a notorious outlaw comes to grips with his past, he reconnects with his estranged daughter and gets one more shot to make things right.
Four overachieving friends spend the summer after finishing high school doing everything possible to enjoy the party life and ruin their reputations.
As Tommy Egan pilots armed drones over Afghanistan from the safe comfort of Las Vegas, the remote nature of his work begins to raise moral questions.
Seeking an apartment to share with his wife, an apolitical man starts to question his own modest goals as revolution swirls around him.
Veteran television newsman Edward R. Murrow faces off against Sen. Joseph McCarthy and his crusade to quell the threat of communism in America.
A struggling couple can't believe their luck when they find a stash of money in the apartment of a neighbor who was recently murdered.
Former mobster Henry Hill recounts his colorful yet violent rise and fall in a New York crime family – a high-rolling dream turned paranoid nightmare.
When he's seen dispatching a rude opposing hockey player in the stands, Doug Glatt is hired by a rival team ... for his fighting skills.
Three teens spend their Halloween trying to stop a magical book, which brings characters from the "Goosebumps" novels to life.
In this witty whodunit, wealthy guests and their servants gather for a weekend stay at the home of Sir William McCordle, who is soon found murdered.
After a car crash, a criminal psychiatrist awakens to find that she's a patient in the same mental institution that currently employs her.

Titulo: Gour Hari Dastaan: The Freedom File
Enredo: A former freedom fighter is forced to navigate the corridors of a disinterested bureaucracy to prove that he fought in India's freedom movement.
A newly widowed Korean War veteran faces his racism and his past when the son of the Hmong family next door tries to steal his beloved 1972 Gran Torino.
Leaving their wives at home, three randy friends look forward to some raunchy extramarital fun at their college reunion.
Good girl Cam recruits her pot-loving bestie Jinky to help deliver a backpack full of weed for her drug-dealing fiancé.
John Travolta and Olivia Newton-John star in this hit musical comedy about a greaser and the good girl he falls for – much to his friends' chagrin.
At the end of their low-budget tour, a punk band accepts a gig at an isolated rural club, only to discover that their hosts are neo-Nazis.

Titulo: Green White Green (And All the Beautiful Colours in My Mosaic of Madness)
Enredo: Three young Nigerian bohemians, each from one of the country's major ethnic groups, explore the directions in which their lives could go.

Titulo: Gringo: The Dangerous Life of John McAfee
Enredo: Tech tycoon John McAfee made millions from his anti-virus software. Now, he may be best known for his bizarre and scandalous lifestyle.
Filmmakers follow a Colorado family's highly public battle for the rights of their transgender daughter, Coy, in a landmark civil rights case.
Two roaming Kenyan bandits attempt to change the course of their lives by exchanging their rifles for running shoes.

Titulo: Guy Martin: Last Flight of the Vulcan Bomber
Enredo: Guy Martin assists in preparing the last airworthy Vulcan bomber for a farewell tour while revealing the stories behind the iconic aircraft.
When an earthquake hits Chile, rescue workers must put aside their differences to save the country from a businessman's evil scheme.
When an uneducated mother of eight suddenly becomes mayor, she uses the skills she's learned as a housewife to keep her town running like clockwork.
In 1949, with freedoms threatened, housewife Hükümet is unaware of her future life in politics as she faces off with liar and mayoral hopeful Faruk.
The son of an astrologer faces opposition from his superstitious father regarding his scheme of launching a mango business.
A young woman recovering poorly from a bad romance gets a new lease on life after encountering a handsome man during a job interview.
In 1962, ambitious plus-size teen Tracy Turnblad tries to integrate a racially divided Baltimore one Watusi at a time.
This anthology features seven independent anime shorts from renowned directors, delving into the futuristic universe of the video game franchise Halo.
Witness the origins of Master Chief and the Spartan program as a group of children transform into enhanced soldiers and fight a powerful alien threat.
Love blooms when kind-hearted Avinash takes in Preeti, a woman shunned by society, but the unorthodox living situation creates quite a stir among the neighbors.
The Vietnam War's horrors come brutally to life through the eyes of American soldiers trying to take a heavily fortified hill under Vietcong control.
When a con man tries to retrieve a bag of money, he swoons for a woman with ties to a notorious crew of criminals.
A homicide detective, a criminal profiler and a journalist team up to nab a serial killer whose murders are inspired by the classic game of Hangman.

Titulo: Hank: Five Years from the Brink
Enredo: From Joe Berlinger, director of the "Paradise Lost" trilogy, comes this documentary about controversial former U.S. Treasury Secretary Henry Paulson.
In this concert film, Oscar-winning composer Hans Zimmer performs his most iconic movie scores to a sell-out crowd at the O2 Arena in Prague.
On the run from his meth-dealing employers, a drifter with a drinking problem becomes prey in a desert town's twisted hunting contest.
Desperate to break up with his clingy girlfriend, a nerdy cartoonist hires a mysterious agency to do the deed. But the agency has unusual methods.
A drug dealer who's been emulating his father's successful criminal career is forced to go on the run with a young girl in this fact-based thriller.

Titulo: Harlem Globetrotters: The Team That Changed the World
Enredo: Relive the greatest moments of the Harlem Globetrotters with this documentary that chronicles the team's legendary 1948 defeat over the Minneapolis Lakers and their historic 1951 Berlin trip.

Titulo: Harold and Lillian: A Hollywood Love Story
Enredo: Storyboard artist Harold Michelson and his film researcher wife, Lillian, recall the influence they had on 60 years of Hollywood's biggest hits.
Intrepid writer Harriet Welsch is determined to become the class blogger despite stiff competition from her snooty archrival.
With only a strong will and a cheap horse, a former agent of the Dutch underground in World War II sets out to become a champion show jumper.
This film chronicles the career of photographer Harry Benson, who earned global renown with his candid shots of the Beatles and other celebrities.
A millionaire opens the door to comic complications when he punishes his spoiled sons for trying to make money through shady, get-rich-quick schemes.

Titulo: Haunters: The Art of the Scare
Enredo: This documentary takes us into the world of those who create horror simulations for willing audiences, and examines the culture they have spawned.
When a fraternity's last big luau serves up horrible deaths to its partygoers, the brothers learn firsthand about their house’s frightening history.
This documentary paints a candid picture of Australian street artist Anthony Lister as he navigates his burgeoning career and personal hardships.
An alcoholic with a tragic past rents an apartment in a building for those in recovery, but soon learns the truth about residents who get "evicted."
A last-minute mission in Dublin turns deadly for stunning secret operative Mallory Kane when she realizes she's been betrayed.
This documentary tells the story of a teenage Pakistani girl shot for her advocacy of women's education, her survival, and her continued efforts.
A group of college students on a weekend getaway accidentally summon a supernatural entity intent on using them for its deadly ritual.
This edgy drama follows 19-year-old Ari, a gay Greek-Australian whose roiling ethnic- and sexual-identity struggles lead to a wild, 24-hour odyssey.
In this stylish comedy, a mother-daughter con team makes money the old-fashioned way: They use their feminine wiles to swindle it.
A shy, brilliant boy and a popular girl fall into an unexpected romance. But as their bond deepens, his attraction begins taking on dark overtones.
When a hedgehog suffering from memory loss forgets his identity, he ends up on a big city journey with a pigeon to save his habitat from a human threat.
When best friends break a blood oath, one of them is cast away to hell, and the other two must save him from the misfits of the underworld.
Love comes to a lonely writer in the sleekest of packages when he finds himself falling for the advanced operating system he bought to run his life.
A woman must decide if she’s willing to end her pregnancy to save her own life after being diagnosed with breast cancer.
The bond between two crooks and best friends is threatened when one learns that the other's father had a hand in his own tragic past.
When she finally encounters two other survivors, a woman alone in a world decimated by a zombie epidemic struggles to trust her new companions.
While serving as the marshal of rowdy Abilene, Kansas, "Wild Bill" Hickok uses guns and gall to tidy up the lawless frontier town.

Years after an accident at a wild Christmas party traumatized them all, six former friends find themselves trapped in a shopping mall and forced by a killer disguised as Santa Claus to play a lethal game of hide-and-seek.
While living a comfortable life with his wife and child, a germophobic man realizes his estranged brother may have committed a terrible crime.
Fiery passions take center stage in this intimate look at the Australian String Quartet and, perhaps more vital, the priceless instruments they guard.
This detailed examination of the 1945 Hiroshima bombing includes the prelude to and aftermath of history's controversial first use of atomic weapons.
In a plot to bait the snake-goddess Nagin for her immortality-granting essence, George States journeys to India and abducts her reptilian lover.
Smooth and sexy Hitch helps clients make a great first impression on a date, but he's thrown when a lovely reporter starts nosing around his business.
Hitler, Nazi propaganda and 1936 Berlin Olympics are put under the microscope to uncover hidden truths and the historical legacy of those games.
Trace the history of Hitler's armored private train, a 15-car mobile headquarters boasting state-of-the-art communications and anti-aircraft cannons.
Three friends in modern-day Karachi navigate their post-college lives, while struggling to balance their passion for music with familial obligations.
Trying to resurrect his career, not-so-talented magician Iskender goes on tour, but things get iffy when one of his illusions works a little too well.
Eight gleefully grim short tales set on Halloween, Mother's Day, St. Patrick's Day and other holidays comprise this chilling horror anthology.
An ex-member charts his path from idealism to disenchantment in a California cult when alarming revelations about the group's leader come to light.
Former rap musician Joey Boy is now a monk who takes Father Teng's place at his rural temple, where a crisis develops involving a nearby stone quarry.
Two new monks, one of them a former rock music star seeking inner peace, join a temple plagued by thieves who are stealing its valuable holy relics.
In the forests of Karnataka, a farmer and his community face eviction from the land when they get caught in the currents of socio-political change.
Determined to trace her ancestral history, an Armenian woman travels to a French village, where she befriends a kind man and, better yet, finds herself.
Determined to prove herself as a street dancer, Maria heads from juvie to a Bronx rec center where she's introduced to her dance idol, Honey Daniels.
Despite discouragement from her loved ones, a talented street dancer tries out for an exclusive dance crew in a bid to win a college scholarship.
Fresh off a top-secret training, feisty heroine Little Red teams up with intrepid reporter Wolf to investigate the disappearance of Hansel and Gretel.
When a teen with terminal cancer miraculously finds herself in remission, she struggles to give up the attention her illness gave her at school.
The remarkable true story of Gift Ngoepe, the first African to play for Major League Baseball, is recounted in this inspiring documentary.
On a dare, seven college friends spend a night at an abandoned hotel rumored to be haunted and find themselves trapped in a nightmare.
Follow the eerie story of Father Malachi Martin, a disenchanted priest whose belief in demonic possession would lead him to conduct several exorcisms.
Witnesses recount the shocking 1996 hostage crisis in Lima, Peru, where rebels held scores of high-level figures captive at an ambassador's residence.
Two teenage geeks inadvertently find a lifelike, state-of-the-art sex robot, but must dodge the high-profile owner who lost her in order to keep her.
When a resourceful but flighty Londoner is threatened with eviction, she vows to do whatever it takes to defeat a greedy real estate agent.
A motivated teen strives to rise from dishwasher to waiter at a luxury hotel only to tread in the abusive tide of its workplace hierarchy.
It's love at first sight for Dracula when he meets Ericka, the charming but mysterious captain of the monster cruise that Mavis plans for the family.

Titulo: House at the End of the Street
Enredo: Moving to a new town proves even more stressful for a teenager when she learns that the house next door was the site of a double murder.
Featuring archival footage and exclusive interviews, this documentary looks at the rise, fall and comeback of charismatic fashion designer Zac Posen.
Blending fact with myth, this conspiracy-minded docufiction argues that the U.S. purchased Yugoslavia's secret space program in the 1960s.

Titulo: How the Beatles Changed the World
Enredo: Interviews and rare archival footage illuminate how the Beatles' influence over music and culture continues to be felt around the world.
The Grinch decides to rob Whoville of Christmas – but a dash of kindness from little Cindy Lou Who and her family may be enough to melt his heart.

Titulo: How to Be a Latin Lover
Enredo: When an aging Lothario gets the boot from his sugar mama, he must pull out all the stops to find a new female sponsor.
Dray lives life one woman at a time and is the envy of all his friends, until his sister decides to show him the error of his philandering ways.
In the 1970s, a group of activists who gathered to protest nuclear testing formed the iconic Greenpeace environmental organization.

Titulo: How to Make an American Quilt
Enredo: A conflicted young woman spends the summer with her grandmother, her great-aunt and their quilting circle, whose life stories captivate her.

Titulo: How to Win the US Presidency
Enredo: This whimsical look at rough-and-tumble American politics examines the influence of money, religion and even ancient Rome on presidential campaigns.
A schoolteacher known for his good deeds and benevolence takes a walk on the dark side after undergoing a heart transplant.
This action-packed animated double feature pits the Hulk against two of the Marvel Universe's most powerful characters: Wolverine and Thor.
A scheming matriarch plots to cut off her disabled stepson and his wife from the family fortune, creating a division within the clan.
Two kindred spirits who are betrothed to others must decide whether to go through with arranged marriages or brush aside convention for true love.
While filming his daily life for a media course, Cowen discovers his small English town may be under an ominous and otherworldly influence.
A hired gun has second thoughts when he's contracted to kill a teenage girl whose father's shady business dealings put her life in danger.
Fired for being gay, schoolteacher Richard returns in drag as force-of-nature Bianca, gets hired for the same job and plots sweet, scornful revenge.

Titulo: Hurricane Bianca: From Russia With Hate
Enredo: When Texas teacher Richard is lured to Russia under false pretenses by his enemy Deb, his drag alter ego Bianca soon turns the country upside down.
A pimp with aspirations of grandeur wants to make it as a rapper but discovers that fame isn't all it's cracked up to be in this indie drama.
A young actress rehearsing for a play about human trafficking begins to relive terrifying scenes that may be dreams – or an alternate reality.
Four individuals in modern India grapple with their identities amid social taboos, trauma and brutal sexual discrimination in this quartet of stories.
Mixing archival footage with present-day interviews, Olympic champion and global icon Usain Bolt opens up about his athletic legacy.
This intense documentary follows real cases of American girls enslaved in the child sex trade through ads in a newspaper's online classified section.
Through her own words and art, a young woman details the healing power of yoga in her struggle with anorexia and her journey to self-acceptance.
A North Korean propagandist who escaped to Seoul now creates satirical art about Kim Jong Il's regime and copes with repercussions of his defection.
After learning that an ex-military friend and his parents were killed, the highly trained John Gold comes to town seeking answers and revenge.
Hell-bent on avenging his wife's murder, Stanley Hill summons an old partner's help in exposing a cover-up by crooked cops and slimy politicians.

Titulo: I Don't Know How She Does It
Enredo: In this affable yuppie comedy, Kate Reddy is a successful executive, wife and mom whose personal and professional lives hang in precarious balance.
Experience the joy and sacrifice of one of the nation's premier dance companies as its members and instructors prepare for a prestigious competition.

Titulo: I Fine... Thank You... Love You
Enredo: Desperate to go to the U.S. to win back his girlfriend, Yim hires a tutor to teach him English. But things don't go according to plan.
While fighting for his welfare benefits following a job-ending heart attack, a widowed carpenter befriends a single mother in a similar plight.
Four hundred years after they were frozen in time, a Ming Dynasty guard and his three pursuers are defrosted to continue their ancient battle.
After an actor is hit by a car driven by the police commissioner's sister, his scheming brother-in-law files a bogus suit against the commissioner.
Igor, the brilliant but deformed assistant to mad Dr. Glickenstein, dreams of winning the Evil Science Fair and the heart of village beauty Gretchen.
This anthology illustrates the timeless nature of desire in four stories of incest, bloodlust and other forbidden subjects.
With little oxygen left in their scuba tanks, two sisters are trapped in a shark cage at the bottom of the ocean while great whites circle nearby.
Grief-stricken over the death of his true love, singer-songwriter Metin has given up on life, until he meets Gizem, who slowly reawakens his heart.
When an imprisoned terrorist cell hijacks a high-security prison in outer space, a CIA agent becomes the one chance of stopping them.
A man returns to his childhood hometown, where he meets the happily married woman he once jilted, while his best friend endures a more volatile union.
In the streets of Senegal, a youth movement rises up against a regime bent on retaining power in this chronicle of the nation's stormy 2012 elections.
When Elastigirl gets recruited for a high-profile crime-fighting mission, Mr. Incredible takes on his toughest assignment ever: full-time parenting.
A man buys a young girl, code-names her "Doll" and sends her to live with a mother of two who has a mysterious mission to be fulfilled.

Titulo: Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull
Enredo: Indiana Jones is drawn into a Russian plot to unearth the Crystal Skulls of Akator, Amazonian artifacts with supernatural powers.

Titulo: Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade
Enredo: Accompanied by his father, Indiana Jones sets off on his third adventure to explore the cradle of civilization on a perilous hunt for the Holy Grail.

Titulo: Indiana Jones and the Raiders of the Lost Ark
Enredo: When Indiana Jones is hired by the government to locate the legendary Ark of the Covenant, he finds himself up against the entire Nazi regime.

Titulo: Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom
Enredo: Indiana Jones, his young sidekick and a spoiled songbird get more than they bargained for when they go to India in search of a missing magical stone.
After a weekend fling with artist Victor, Veronica, a psychiatrist and politician's wife, becomes the target of Victor's dangerous romantic obsession.
Former U.S. Labor Secretary Robert Reich makes a compelling case about the serious crisis the U.S. faces due to the widening economic gap.
Italians in London reveal the ups and downs of immigration and touch upon their uneasiness about leaving behind their crisis-ridden homeland.
A Jewish cinema owner in occupied Paris is forced to host a Nazi premiere, where a group of American soldiers called the Basterds plans a face-off.
Unbeknownst to his 12-year-old daughter, a bookbinder has a secret ability to bring characters to life by reading their stories out loud.
A grieving policeman and a rickshaw driver are brought together by a dark, tragic secret that will change their lives forever.
Unable to locate the elusive mother of a baby girl left on his doorstep, an Acapulco playboy unexpectedly begins to develop feelings for the tot.
Five viral Internet celebrities travel to a competition that will award one of them their own television series in this ensemble comedy.
In the near future, two frightened sisters fight for survival after losing their father during a deadly, quietly looming apocalypse.

Titulo: Inuyasha the Movie - L'isola del fuoco scarlatto
Enredo: Ai, a young half-demon who has escaped from Horai Island to try to help his people, returns with potential saviors InuYasha, Sesshomaru and Kikyo.

Titulo: Inuyasha the Movie - La spada del dominatore del mondo
Enredo: The Great Dog Demon beaqueathed one of the Three Swords of the Fang to each of his two sons. Now the evil power of the third sword has been awakened.

Titulo: InuYasha: The Movie 2: The Castle Beyond the Looking Glass
Enredo: With their biggest foe seemingly defeated, InuYasha and his friends return to everyday life. But the peace is soon shattered by an emerging new enemy.
After the end of apartheid, newly elected President Nelson Mandela uses the 1995 World Cup rugby matches to unite his people in South Africa.
Artists and writers delve into the heart of Antoine de Saint-Exupéry's timeless fable, which captured the imagination of children and adults worldwide.
At an initiation ritual for the young men of his Xhosa community, a closeted factory hand meets a Johannesburg teen who discovers his best-kept secret.
A boy with a hearing and speech impairment – and extraordinary athletic ability – chases his lifelong dream of playing cricket for India.
Bored in their happy marriage, a couple decides to spice things up by fighting more, but their game takes the relationship on an unexpected path.

Titulo: Iron Cowboy: The Story of the 50.50.50
Enredo: A record-setting triathlete dares to complete 50 Ironman races – a 2.4-mile swim, a 112-mile bike ride, and a 26.2-mile run – in 50 days in 50 states.
A young millionaire is willing to do anything to make the schoolteacher he loves happy. Even if it means helping her marry someone else.
Two young lovers in Banaras are caught in the crossfire of a feud between their powerful families and a political climate destroying their city.
The Olsen twins put a cute new spin on Mark Twain's classic tale "The Prince and the Pauper," playing identical 9-year-olds from very different backgrounds: orphaned Amanda and wealthy Alyssa.
When a beautiful belly-dancer moves into their apartment building, a group of unhappily married men strives to get her attention.
When Eva and Alex decide to wed in England, where they met three years earlier, obstacles including a labor strike and a volcano keep them apart.
Two down-on-their-luck singers set out to marry wealthy women – but not everyone is happy to have them climb the social ladder.
This unfiltered documentary follows the rocky life and stratospheric career of Allen Iverson, an NBA icon who left an indelible mark on the sport.
Miniforce, a special task force of elite rangers, takes on the Lizard Army to save Earth before it’s too late, in this prequel to the TV series.

Titulo: Jaan-E-Mann: Let's Fall in Love... Again
Enredo: To avoid alimony payments, an aspiring actor schemes for his ex-wife to marry an unlikely suitor, but soon realizes he may not be ready to lose her.
Equipped with a mechanical heart and determined to stay out of death's shadow, young Jack understands that love could prove fatal.
Once upon a time, baseball cards were as much an American pastime as the sport. But then scandal rocked the multi-million-dollar industry for good.
When an aging flight attendant's caught smuggling cash and forced to help with an investigation, she hatches a clever plan to make off with the dough.
A lottery ticket salesperson faces an ethical dilemma after setting aside a soon-to-be winning ticket for a customer to pick up and pay for later.
Incarcerated for a crime he didn’t commit, a young man must navigate the crowded, cut-throat environment of prison as he awaits trial.
Jake, Izzy, Cubby and Skully face off against the scheming Captain Hook in a race to find special treasures hidden all around Never Land.
A gifted young man from a drought-stricken village helps a group of ecologists find water for migrating flamingoes.
When they travel to their father's ancestral village, city kids expecting a natural paradise instead find a poor, dusty town that harbors secrets.
After 11 years in Canada, young Meena returns to her native Pakistan for a family wedding and becomes romantically entangled with an adopted cousin.

Titulo: Jay and Silent Bob Strike Back
Enredo: Jay and Silent Bob's comic book alter egos have been sold to Hollywood without permission, so they head to Tinseltown to sabotage the production.
Tormented by mistrust, a businessman hires a cagey tailor to track his wife's whereabouts with her doctor only to send his mind further down an abyss.
The journey of fashion designer Jeremy Scott from humble roots on a Missouri farm to creative director of Moschino is charted in this documentary.
Adapted from the hit Broadway musical, this nostalgic look at the Four Seasons and their bumpy offstage lives stretches across four decades.
Host Hugh Bonneville traces Jesus' last days to learn how the execution of an itinerant Jewish preacher had an immense impact on society.
The story of famed L.A. nightclub Catch One and owner Jewel Thais-Williams, who defied all odds and provided a safe space for black LGBT communities.
Jimi Hendrix's family, friends, and fellow musicians discuss his life and influence. Hendrix also appears in classic performance footage.
This documentary profiles sushi chef Jiro Ono, an 85-year-old master whose 10-seat, $300-a-plate restaurant is legendary among Tokyo foodies.

Titulo: Jis Desh Men Ganga Behti Hai
Enredo: Falling in with a band of outlaws during a holy pilgrimage, a country boy tries to change their violent ways ahead of a showdown with the authorities.

Titulo: Joe Cocker: Mad Dog with Soul
Enredo: From his star turn at Woodstock to his battles with addiction, this film chronicles the stormy life and unique talent of soulful singer Joe Cocker.
Truth and fiction blend in this quasi-documentary about six exhausted workers at a Mumbai call center servicing U.S. customers.
A bank manager and his wife, still grieving over their daughter who died in a fire, become pawns in a bank heist with ties to corruption and fraud.
Iconic rocker John Mellencamp lights up Chicago in an electrifying live performance featuring old classics and new tracks.
Two siblings share a body, each getting it for 12 hours a day. But when one of them breaks the rules, their whole way of life comes crashing down.
The wounds of a traumatic childhood and a corrupt, unjust system push a young man into becoming a cold-blooded, ruthless gangster.
Separated at birth, a pair of identical twins unexpectedly reunite as adults and embark on a madcap mission to take down a common enemy from their past.

Titulo: Judy Moody and the Not Bummer Summer
Enredo: In this family film, never-dull third-grader Judy Moody embarks on a summer adventure with her brother, Stink, and always-up-for-fun Aunt Opal.
Following the stories of five diverse individuals, this documentary offers a glimpse into the indomitable tenacity of several Mumbai residents.
After a whirlwind romance, a couple rushes to say "I do" at the bride's family estate on Martha's Vineyard, where their relations meet — and clash.
When a big-city art dealer travels to North Carolina to meet her new husband's small-town family, their trip gives rise to a multitude of problems.
Years after high school, a once-portly nice guy comes home for the holidays and reunites with a former crush he still has feelings for.
Teen idol Justin Bieber provides personal snapshots from throughout his career, culminating with scenes from his triumphant 2010 concert tour.
On board Russia's first nuclear ballistic submarine, Capt. Vostrikov must race against time to prevent a Chernobyl-like explosion.
The happy life of a young blind couple is shattered when the wife is raped and corrupt police won't help, sending the husband on a quest for revenge.
Star-crossed lovers from different social strata struggle to overcome differences in class and family expectation, as well as a long separation.
Jailed for robbing his brother’s unscrupulous employer, a simpleton has a transformation while in prison, emerging with a violent mission for revenge.
In this Hindi version of the Tamil blockbuster, a Tamil gang leader in Kuala Lumpur seeks justice for crimes committed against him and his family.
A troubled young girl and her mother find solace on a journey with a subversive poet whose words captivate their hearts and imaginations.
A popular singer on the run poses as a bartender and falls in love with a prostitute, but their love is threatened by a violent incident in his past.
A quiet ex-con's tenuous grip on reality starts to slip when his manipulative mother brings out a part of him he hoped to leave behind.
A scientist trying to solve one of the universe's greatest puzzles begins a romance with a much younger colleague that's haunted by a dark secret.
A doctor and his colleagues who use sex-determination testing for unethical ends face retribution from a supernatural victim who seeks vengeance.
When flashbacks reveal that he's the reincarnation of a man murdered by his wife, rock star Monty sets out to get revenge for the decades-old crime.
A present-day woman takes responsibility for guiding a charming time-traveling 19th-century nobleman through the 21st century.
Secretly in love with his neighbor, a mild-mannered clerk is heartbroken when his much bolder, more charming friend wins her heart instead.
Outspoken comedian Katt Williams pokes fun at a variety of topics, including sex, relationships, parenthood and trying to make it as an entertainer.
When a late poet leaves behind his property to a young man, the man's brother suspects the poet may have been more than just a family friend.
Wrongfully accused of murder, two students' last hope lies with their defense attorney, an inexperienced bumbler who's never even tried a case.

Titulo: Kevin Hart: Laugh at My Pain
Enredo: Sometimes edgy and always hilarious, comedian Kevin Hart shines in this theatrical version of his record-breaking 2011 live tour.
Philadelphia funnyman Kevin Hart takes the stage in front of a sold-out crowd at Madison Square Garden, part of his hit "Let Me Explain" world tour.

Titulo: Kevyn Aucoin: Beauty & the Beast in Me
Enredo: Makeup artist Kevyn Aucoin worked with top supermodels in the 1980s and 1990s. Personal videos merged with interviews provide a peek into his life.
A prison guard goes undercover as a dancer to try and recapture an escaped criminal and restore her police inspector boyfriend's reputation.
A cranky control freak must rely on his comically dysfunctional family to pull off a scam on a greedy land shark who's stolen his prized property.
A strict matriarch's regimented household is upended by the arrival of a spunky relative who challenges the rules.
While playing matchmaker to a pair of their friends, two young university students begin developing feelings for each other.
A 15-year-old girl with autism attempts to write a mystery novel based on her hunt for the killer of a neighborhood cat.
Sloan's vow to never return to Thailand is cut short when he's kidnapped and taken to a Thai prison, where he's forced to fight a 400-pound brute.
After a skilled fighter falls in the ring, his younger brother emerges from the shadows to train and get revenge against a brutal champion.
Growing up in poverty and political turmoil, he found his way out in the ring. The early years of world-famous boxer Manny Pacquiao unfolds in this biopic.
When beer magnate Alfred "Freddy" Heineken is kidnapped in 1983, his abductors make the largest ransom demand in history.
An assassin is shot by her ruthless employer, Bill, and other members of their assassination circle. But she lives – and plots her vengeance.
The Bride has three left on her rampage list: Budd, Elle Driver and Bill himself. But when she arrives at Bill's house, she's in for a surprise.
On a remote island, elite soldiers discover their training exercise is actually an experimental death trap teeming with efficiently lethal robots.

Titulo: Kill Hitler! The Luck of the Devil
Enredo: From politicians to officers, many attempted to kill Hitler – and failed. This documentary delves into the details of how their plots unraveled.
Posing as a telecom salesman at a business conference, a CIA agent fights to protect a fledgling Eastern European democracy from a military coup.
An alien band of killer clowns descends from the cosmos to harvest scores of small-town victims, cocooning their prey in cotton candy to eat later.
After a whirlwind romance, Jen and Spencer settle into married life — until Spencer's secret past as a hit man shakes up their suburban bliss.
Two young men with disabilities befriend a hitman in a wheelchair and become his helpers, only to wind up in the crosshairs of a Serbian mobster.
On patrol in Afghanistan, a British paratrooper unit unwittingly ventures into a dry riverbed that turns out to be littered with land mines.
Already coping with a bully, a mercurial older brother and summer school, 15-year-old Jack is saddled with his young cousin for an eventful weekend.

A wealthy, despicable businessman comes to the realization that he may lose half his fortune to the obnoxious wife he's trying to divorce. So, he decides to arrange his own kidnapping in order to wipe himself out and claim poverty.
A foster mom and her houseful of kids befriend a bitter neighbor after the Rodney King verdict is handed down in 1992 Los Angeles.
A man's decision to marry three women, to keep them from committing suicide, complicates his relationship with his girlfriend.
A forensic psychologist teams up with an escaped kidnapping victim to hunt down a serial killer who abducts and dominates strong-willed women.
A field hockey-playing pizza delivery boy finds himself transformed from slacker to zombie slayer during an outbreak of the undead in Kuala Lumpur.
A devoted husband and father on his own for the weekend has his life turned inside out after giving shelter to two young women during a storm.
Though culturally insensitive by modern standards, this propaganda film examines the history of Japan from the 16th century through the 1930s.
Witness the incredible, decades-long friendship between Koko the gorilla and Penny Patterson, who taught Koko to communicate via sign language.
With five loyal friends in tow, explorer Thor Heyerdahl sails a fragile balsa wood raft along an ancient path some 4,300 miles across the Pacific.
A speech and hearing-impaired couple persists through unforgiving obstacles to be accepted by society and live a life of dignity.
When he sets out to avenge his son's murder, mild-mannered snowplow driver Nils sparks a war between a Norwegian mobster and his Serbian rival.
A team of minstrels, including a monkey, cat and donkey, narrate folktales from the Indian regions of Rajasthan, Kerala and Punjab.

Titulo: Krish Trish and Baltiboy: Battle of Wits
Enredo: An artisan is cheated of his payment, a lion of his throne and a brother of his inheritance in these three stories of deception and justice.

Titulo: Krish Trish and Baltiboy: Best Friends Forever
Enredo: A cat, monkey and donkey team up to narrate folktales about friendship from Northeast India, and the Indian regions of Bihar and Rajasthan.

Titulo: Krish Trish and Baltiboy: Comics of India
Enredo: In three comic-strip-style tales, a boy tries to sell wisdom, a demon is released from captivity, and a king assigns impossible tasks to his minister.

Titulo: Krish Trish and Baltiboy: Face Your Fears
Enredo: In three tales about fear, a baby elephant gets captured by a circus, two boys enter a haunted house and a parrot faces his fear of flying.

Titulo: Krish Trish and Baltiboy: Oversmartness Never Pays
Enredo: A cat, monkey and donkey learn the consequences of cheating through stories from the Indian regions of Rajasthan, West Bengal and Maharashtra.

Titulo: Krish Trish and Baltiboy: Part II
Enredo: Animal minstrels narrate stories about a monkey's friendship with a crocodile, two monkeys' foolishness and a villager's encounter with a demon.

Titulo: Krish Trish and Baltiboy: The Greatest Trick
Enredo: The consequences of trickery are explored in stories involving an inconsiderate husband, two greedy courtiers, and a kind man who loses everything.
After 10 years away from her family, Krisha returns for Thanksgiving, but bitter grudges and troubling addictions threaten to ruin the event.
Opting to stay on campus over the Thanksgiving holiday, coed Justine and a handful of friends find their break violently disrupted by a sadistic gang.
A kid with a heart condition falls for an ex-stripper with a lot of baggage and joins her Alcoholics Anonymous group to catch her attention.

Titulo: Kuldip Patwal: I Didn't Do It!
Enredo: Accused of killing a politician, a local grocer’s fight to prove his innocence reveals his lifelong struggles with injustice leading up to the incident.
Sing, a mobster in 1940s China, longs to be as cool as the formally clad Axe Gang, a band of killers who rule Hong Kong, but can only pretend.
Shortsighted curmudgeon Mr. Magoo and his young nephew, Justin, fight such nefarious foes as kung fu villains, robot spiders and teenage mutants.
As preparations for the Winter Feast build, Po is caught between his obligations as the Dragon Warrior and his family holiday traditions.
Two mismatched archaeologists battle a team of vicious mercenaries in a race to discover an ancient Tibetan treasure of unimaginable worth.
This film charts Nirvana's Kurt Cobain's rise to fame, his drug-addled romance with Courtney Love and the conspiracy theories surrounding his death.
When a recently single psychologist moves to a new neighborhood, she finds friendship with women starting to rebel against years of domestic abuse.
A young university student's world is shaken after her brief involvement with a wealthy playboy results in her pregnancy.

Titulo: Kygo: Live at the Hollywood Bowl
Enredo: Join Norwegian electronic music superstar Kygo onstage and behind the scenes as he performs at the famed L.A. venue with a bevy of special guests.
Cinematic lovebirds Aishwarya Rai and Vivek Oberoi star in this love story about a sweet young girl, Diya, brought up by her widowed father on a coffee plantation in the village of Coorg.
Three best buddies are thrown into a wild chase for a priceless painting that was stolen from a house they used to throw a huge party.
Previously unseen footage is shaped into a fresh and timely retelling of the 1992 Rodney King trial – and the verdict that sparked civil unrest.
The plane crash that killed Buddy Holly also took Ritchie Valens, whose modest upbringing and rise to fame are depicted in this exhilarating biopic.
After winning a shared trip to a soccer match, two colleagues who hold opposite world views find they're stuck traveling together for the duration.
Eager for cash, Rajesh joins his friend Shankar's blood-theft operation. As Rajesh's greed grows and the cops close in, Shankar is poised to explode.
